AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202052_From_Role101: With all that said, I am serious about this decision!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202044_From_Role101: I've given it some thought. I'm going to make an important decision...
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204025_From_Role101: When will my superiors become more open-minded? I heard they were planning to visit me today to talk about it... Why must it be today of all days? I just want to play the new game in peace!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203071_From_Role101: Sorry. You must have been worried.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row51101020_PlayerOption_ToRole101: I'm taking you to a mysterious event...
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203058_From_Role101: Investigator Michele coming to your rescue!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203040_From_OtherRole: Investigator, fulfill your duty and lock down the site. Prevent the spread of the erosion flow and await further instructions! Over.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203036_From_OtherRole: Investigator Michele, lock-down and secure the site immediately. Await backup with erosive substance collection equipment. Over.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202030_From_OtherRole: The Sentinel Bureau has started disciplinary action against her father as a result of his incompetence in handling the Port Euler case, resulting in the department losing a significant amount of personnel. His superiors have decided to suspend him from frontline work.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102037_From_Role101: I don't want to give up on either of them. I am the unique super gamer investigator!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204016_PlayerOption_ToRole101: Are you hiding something from me?
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204005_From_Role101: Really? But today is not my birthday...
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203027_From_Role101: It's extremely dangerous! Erosion substances are a type of harmful liquid produced during stringification! Contact with it is lethal!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204008_PlayerOption_ToRole101: The new game will be released today!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204439_PlayerOption_ToRole101: Your gamer's mindset has saved everyone!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101101013_From_Role101: We have "Paper Detective," a candidate for Best Story of the Year, and "Superheroes of Justice", a classic action game that continues childhood memories. Which one would you like to play?
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201039_From_Role101: It's too late. We have both died from the poison... We've lost all the equipment and items we collected along the way...
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204011_From_Role101: Based on the latest update, it should be delivered today. Let's play it together once it arrives.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202021_From_Role101: Eh? I've met him before. He's a newly promoted investigator from the second squad, my junior from the academy. Back then, he and I were assigned to the same combat drill team.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row51101004_From_Role101: Eh? Partner, when did you get here? Can you teleport?
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102004_From_Role101: Since neither of us is on the clock right now, let's forget about work!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101101016_From_Role101: And guess what? They gave it to us for free. Let's dive in and see what it feels like to be a "Great Detective"!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201034_From_Role101: The dragon's running out of HP. We're about to win!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102042_From_Role101: After all, a protagonist needs companions, right, my best gaming buddy?
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203074_From_Role101: After all, our duel has yet to start!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row51101019_PlayerOption_ToRole101: No time to explain. Come with me.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203077_From_Role101: The arcade will probably be closed for a while.
AVGEvent_Michel.101202000_PrologueTitle: To Be a Gamer or Ordinary
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101101010_From_Role101: An investigator by day, gamer by night. Does that seem a bit odd to you?
AVGEvent_Michel.101201000_PrologueTitle: A Day in the Life of a Gamer
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102035_From_Role101: I am no longer alone because I've met you, Navigator, my new gaming buddy!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201031_From_Role101: So far, so good. These monsters are weak.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row51101018_From_Role101: Judging from your expression, I feel like you're going to do something astonishing or announce important news...
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102015_From_Role101: They remind me of my own - Mighty Meow and Pawtector!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row51101007_From_Role101: R-Really? I totally didn't notice you...
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202014_From_Role101: Just when I thought I had them, I walked right into a trap and lost my target. My gamer's mindset doesn't work every time...
AVGEvent_Michel.Row51101022_From_Role101: Wait a moment, partner. Let me put down the pen and paper... W-Where are you taking me?
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204049_From_Role101: Thanks for your patience. A brand-new adventure featuring the navigator and the investigator is about to start!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202033_From_Role101: Dad is not like that! He was transferred from field duty because of the injuries he sustained trying to protect his partner. It had nothing to do with his handling of the case!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101101019_From_Role101: It's time to find out how well we work together as a team. Show me what you've got, Navigator!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203025_PlayerOption_ToRole101: An erosion flow? Is it serious?
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201032_From_Role101: Up ahead is the boss of the first level, one nine-headed venomous dragon lurking underground. Be careful, partner!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203075_From_Role101: It would be a shame for me to perish now, wouldn't it?
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201055_From_Role101: If only my superiors from the Sentinel Bureau were as understanding as you... Would save me from a ton of written apologies...
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102006_From_Role101: That's what I'm going for! You'll know when we get there!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203021_From_OtherRole: Alert! An erosion flow has occurred at 30 Caprivi Street, Area 2, Elmond East. Requesting all nearby officers to respond immediately!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203016_From_Role101: Let's get started. This is going to be the battle to end all battles!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201014_From_Role101: By the way, check out the cartridge! I had to queue all night to get it.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102038_From_Role101: This is embarrassing... But I would like to be a hero a game is based on, just like my father.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101101003_From_Role101: Speaking of games, if you regularly visit The No.1 Gaming Forum, you must have heard of the famous moderator, Super Pawtector. She frequently updates game guides and shares gaming news...
AVGEvent_Michel.Row51101016_From_Role101: Now that I think about it, you've been acting all mysterious...
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204040_PlayerOption_ToRole101: Please have faith in yourself, Investigator Michele.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202048_From_Role101: Thank you, partner... At least one person cares about the gamer Michele.
AVGEvent_Michel.101203000_PrologueTitle: The Way of the Super Gamer
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201029_From_Role101: Enough about the past... Let's get started. I can't wait!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101101018_From_Role101: This series was already popular back on Old Earth. It is a co-op role-playing game.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101101008_From_Role101: How did you tell? You really do have a keen eye.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201026_From_Role101: What a coincidence! I wanted to play Superheroes of Justice with you today!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202029_From_OtherRole: Her father was the hero of the Sentinel Bureau and well-known all across Elmond. But you're aware of the incident, right?
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204639_From_Role101: This is literally the first time someone has thanked me for my gamer's mindset... Turns out I'm awesome!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203007_From_Role101: If we do this, you'll have no more regrets... right?
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202031_From_OtherRole: Such a reckless and incompetent man is no hero!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202011_PlayerOption_ToRole101: I don't think it's as simple as that this time...
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101101015_From_Role101: This is a new text adventure game with a thrilling plot and plenty of suspense based on the TV series of the same name. Even the higher-ups at the investigation unit are recommending it.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201027_From_Role101: I used to play this game with my dad all the time. My favorite character is Mighty Meow, the young dragon slayer!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102011_From_Role101: This is the only cat café in Elmond in collaboration with the No. 1 series. This is the go-to place for fan meetups!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203094_From_Role101: Until next time, then. I'll contact you!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201015_From_Role101: I know you're on the clock, but would you like to try it?
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101101009_From_Role101: Let's get to know each other a bit better, shall we? I work as an investigator, but off the clock, I'm just Michele, the gamer. My ID is Super Pawtector.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101101021_From_Role101: From now on, you'll be my gaming buddy! Here is your controller. Give it a try. You can adjust the sensitivity and shortcut buttons if necessary.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204007_From_Role101: Darn it... Let's try to remember.
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202042_PlayerOption_ToRole101: Who is this hero you speak of?
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202020_Aside_AboutRole101: (A PUS investigator on patrol walks over angrily, looking at us with disdain.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204013_Aside_AboutRole101: (The usually energetic, cat-like girl sounds exhausted, avoiding eye contact with me, giving me a feeling of déjà vu.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203018_Aside_AboutRole101: (A rapid alarm sounds from Michele's portable communication device.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102002_Aside_AboutRole101: (Without any prior work appointments, Michele mysteriously asks to meet.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201142_Aside_AboutRole101: (As if struck by a heavy blow, the disheartened girl hangs her head.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202001_Aside_AboutRole101: (At Grand Beach on my day off.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201242_Aside_AboutRole101: (But after just a second, her blue eyes are filled with a fighting spirit.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203069_Aside_AboutRole101: (But now, she glows like a triumphant warrior.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102009_Aside_AboutRole101: (Holding my hand, the playful girl takes us to a cozy café where several cats are lounging.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204038_Aside_AboutRole101: (The letters read, “To the Cat Investigator, this is a commemorative trophy for players who have pre-ordered the game. It is our pleasure to bestow this honor upon you, whose courage and perseverance is akin to that of the heroes in the game.”
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204339_Aside_AboutRole101: (Many names are signed at the bottom of the letter, followed by a note: “Included are the Mighty Meow Arcade co-branded cat paw cookies. If you like the cookies, please pre-order them as well.”)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201043_Aside_AboutRole101: (Replaying the first level, Michele and I are better coordinated.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203057_Aside_AboutRole101: (Rushing into the arcade, Michele stringifies the shield to block the gushing erosion flow as if she were a shimmer of hope in the darkness.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102013_Aside_AboutRole101: (Several playful cats come to us uninvited, frolicking around Michele.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204101_Aside_AboutRole101: (On another day off, Michele invites to visit her at the familiar Apartment One.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204045_Aside_AboutRole101: (On the other side, I have inserted the disc into the console and picked up the controller ready to start, but Michele is slow to join, staring blankly at her precious trophies.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201017_Aside_AboutRole101: (As I reach for the game console, I notice a familiar item on the coffee table next to the couch.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203067_Aside_AboutRole101: (As the crowd eagerly waits for her to come out, Michele emerges from the smoke, her face covered by ash, but underneath the grime, her smile shines through, bright as ever.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102049_Aside_AboutRole101: (Surrounded by cats, Michele and I stay at the café until late in the evening.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202039_Aside_AboutRole101: (The disheartened girl produces a shiny badge bearing the P.U.S insignia with a sword of justice running through it, as if the bravery and determination of past P.U.S investigators were encapsulated within.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203049_Aside_AboutRole101: (She lifts her head and locks eyes with me, her blue eyes clear as ever.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202037_Aside_AboutRole101: (The man does not dial down his sarcastic tone by a bit. Suddenly, someone calls out for him in the distance, and the man cheerfully runs off.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102008_From_Role101: (Whispering) You're the only person I've ever brought to this place. Please keep it a secret!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204043_From_Role101: (Whispering) Can I become a hero like my dad... That way, his will would not fade away...
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102041_Aside_AboutRole101: (Smiling with joy, the girl looks at me with utmost seriousness.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204026_Aside_AboutRole101: (As the girl frets, sudden, hurried knocks are heard from the door.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202010_Aside_AboutRole101: (The girl who is usually as playful as a kitty seems to have lost all her energy. Deliberately avoiding eye contact with me, she appears unwilling to share her feelings with me.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201002_Aside_AboutRole101: (As invited, I go to Apartment One of PUS in Elmond, where Michele lives. As I open the door, I witness the following scene...)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202028_Aside_AboutRole101: (My wrath is indescribable, but Michele grabs my hands, holding me back, seemingly indifferent to the situation. Is she used to such rumors and slander?)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204001_Aside_AboutRole101: (Through the door, I can hear Michele humming the theme song of Superheroes of Justice. Despite the lively and spirited melody, her voice sounds rather disheartened.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203060_Aside_AboutRole101: (The petite girl holds the shield against the gushing blue-purple erosion flow, as if she were a warrior facing off a flame-spitting dragon.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102001_Aside_AboutRole101: (A few days later, the commercial hub. The weather is clear.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204034_From_Role101: (Sigh of relief) Phew. Let me catch my breath... Alright, I've plucked up courage to open the door!
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201001_Aside_AboutRole101: (One day, Investigator Michele schedules a briefing session with me as soon as she returns from the field.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102033_Aside_AboutRole101: (As we speak, the fluffy fur babies shuffle closely between us, meowing for petting and hugging.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203089_PlayerOption_ToRole101: (I wipe the dust off Michele's face with a tissue.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203004_Aside_AboutRole101: (Michele is excited as well as if this were a regular round of a video game. But try as she might, she cannot hide the reluctance and sadness in her tone.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202038_Aside_AboutRole101: (Michele and I sit on the beach, both of us silent, listening only to the sound of the waves.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204044_Aside_AboutRole101: (Muttering to herself, Michele places the trophy next to the sword and shield models. The three items act as her achievement trophies, shining brightly under the sunlight.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204037_Aside_AboutRole101: (Holding her breath, Michele carefully opens the package, which contains a game trophy filled with cat paw cookies and a letter of appreciation.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203053_Aside_AboutRole101: (Michele vanishes in front of my eyes, rushing to the arcade.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201044_Aside_AboutRole101: (Michele lures the dragon to a hidden trap while I seize the opportunity to cast our ultimate combo: Sword and Shield as One!)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203001_Aside_AboutRole101: (The commercial hub, on the day we agreed to meet.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203062_Aside_AboutRole101: (Though still terrified, the people trapped inside start moving with Michele's encouragement. As they start to pour out of the arcade, Michele is nowhere to be seen.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203063_Aside_AboutRole101: (The blue-purple erosion flow has swallowed the heroine. Just as everyone starts to lose hope, thinking they would never see that light again...)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203043_Aside_AboutRole101: (The blue-purple liquid keeps spilling out. Standing outside the arcade, we can still feel the severity of the situation, worsening by the minute.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203059_Aside_AboutRole101: (Standing outside the arcade entrance, I do not have a clear view of the situation inside, but Michele's brave voice is crystal clear.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201006_Aside_AboutRole101: (Both robo battlecats seem exhausted, slumping next to the charging station, sound asleep. The girl shows no sign of fatigue as if all her energy has been replenished as soon as she returns to the pure world of video games.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201016_Aside_AboutRole101: (I can't say no to the enthusiastic super gamer whose eyes twinkle like little stars.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102050_Aside_AboutRole101: (After an entire day, Michele does not seem tired at all.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101102014_Aside_AboutRole101: (All the cats seem to know her well. With cats all over her, the girl drops her act of slyness and mystery.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203051_Aside_AboutRole101: (Her cute eyes fill with a fighting spirit, sparkling with determination.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201018_Aside_AboutRole101: (It is a shining model of a giant sword. Finely crafted, it resembles the Sword of Light used by Mighty Meow, the protagonist of Superheroes of Justice.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203068_Aside_AboutRole101: (Her cute clothing seems to have been damaged, making her look somewhat disheveled.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101202053_Aside_AboutRole101: (Under the golden sun, against the backdrop of the surging waves, her blue eyes sparkle with determination.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101203055_Aside_AboutRole101: (With a series of clacks, she dismantles and holds the shield prop by the door.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101201045_Aside_AboutRole101: (In an instant, a dazzling golden light emits between the sword and shield, tearing the mighty dragon in half.)
AVGEvent_Michel.Row101204036_Aside_AboutRole101: (Having plucked her courage, the girl flings the door open to find not only the disc of the latest Superheroes of Justice game, but also a mysterious package without the sender's details.)

AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204078_Aside_AboutRole146: (I have to break the silence... Is there anything I can do to divert her attention?)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202066_Aside_AboutRole146: (I recount the event of receiving the package on Celestia's behalf ealier today.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203054_Aside_AboutRole146: (Today, alongside Celestia, we're hosting a public outreach event, endorsed by Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204077_Aside_AboutRole146: (Seemingly realizing this, Celestia appears a bit downhearted.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203049_Aside_AboutRole146: (She seems to have realized something, and her expression brightens up a bit.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204038_Aside_AboutRole146: (The story seems to follow a military Humvee stalling in a war-torn city, igniting a street battle. Celestia is on edge.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204036_Aside_AboutRole146: (It seems to be about a group journeying west to destroy a powerful ring. Celestia is captivated.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204040_Aside_AboutRole146: (It appears to be a horror superhero movie. Celestia is startled several times, almost jumping from her seat.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203030_Aside_AboutRole146: (Every time Celestia talks about her childhood, she seems shy for a moment before returning to her usual calmness.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204100_Aside_AboutRole146: (But the moon and stars continue to shine on the quiet screening area and its final two audiences.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201097_Aside_AboutRole146: (I took the half-broken Star Pad as a memento of my first day at work with Celestia.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204015_Aside_AboutRole146: (Following the officer’s directions, I soon spot Celestia and the volunteers bustling about.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101007_Aside_AboutRole146: (I head to the lounge to meet Celestia, only to find her looking rather gloomy.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202007_Aside_AboutRole146: (I accept the voice message from the delivery robot.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204053_Aside_AboutRole146: (I return to my seat with an excited Celestia. This time, it’s just the two of us.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203062_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia and I take out the bracelets we've made over the past few days and hand them out to the visitors.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203001_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia and I are organizing the medical records of the latest Collapse Syndrome patients.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204026_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia and I chat about the event and movies.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204034_Aside_AboutRole146: (I snap back to reality as Celestia waves and takes her seat beside me. We watch side by side.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204027_Aside_AboutRole146: (As I look around, I realize a lot of people have gathered at the venue.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204012_Aside_AboutRole146: (Unfamiliar with the area, I ask a nearby beach patrol officer for directions.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203025_Aside_AboutRole146: (Not knowing what could be useful, I pick a random item.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201031_Aside_AboutRole146: (Since I'm not familiar with the treatment procedure, I stand aside, carefully observing Celestia's every move.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101049_Aside_AboutRole146: (Amidst joyful cheers, the girl who has always put others before herself finally smiles heartily.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202104_Aside_AboutRole146: (Before the little Sanctuary gets busy again, we quietly enjoy a moment of peace.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204009_Aside_AboutRole146: (After the war, people pray for everlasting peace, hoping that future generations can maintain it better than their forefathers.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201007_Aside_AboutRole146: (The distraught man seems to be exhibiting signs of Collapse Syndrome, so I contact Celestia immediately.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203045_Aside_AboutRole146: (Gently fitting the bracelet on Celestia’s wrist, I adjust it to ensure it's comfortable.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203082_From_Role146: (Whispering) Navigator, would you like to say a few words?
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101019_Aside_AboutRole146: (Is there truly no way to turn this situation around?)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204002_Aside_AboutRole146: (The old film projector clatters as it churns through the reels.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101005_Aside_AboutRole146: (With eager anticipation, I enter Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202036_Aside_AboutRole146: (Fortunately, standing right in front of her, I catch her in time.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204011_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia has invited me to attend Astral Sanctuary's open-air film festival at Grand Beach.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101048_Aside_AboutRole146: (The brilliant colors of the fireworks light up her face... No further explanation is needed.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204054_Aside_AboutRole146: (Time flies. We're down to the last film near midnight.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202052_Aside_AboutRole146: (Suddenly, I notice that the package addressed to Celestia has been opened.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201018_Aside_AboutRole146: (In a daze, I hear Celestia's surprised voice.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204042_Aside_AboutRole146: (As the screenings end, the audience slowly leaves the venue, reminiscing about the stories.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row51146024_Aside_AboutRole146: (I met Celestia's intense gaze and awkwardly began my analysis. Thankfully, everyone cooperated, so my efforts weren’t in vain...)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201029_Aside_AboutRole146: (I help the patient up before explaining the situation to Celestia.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201011_Aside_AboutRole146: (Following Celestia's instructions, I take out the Star Pad she gave me.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201016_Aside_AboutRole146: (Trying to stop the patient from leaving, I accidentally get knocked down by him.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row51146014_Aside_AboutRole146: (Catching my subtle plea for help, the Shop Owner quickly jumped into the conversation.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204031_Aside_AboutRole146: (The screenings mostly feature old Earth films: mystery, sci-fi, spaghetti Westerns... I quickly become engrossed.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201012_Aside_AboutRole146: (The Star Pad is a tablet and an electronic record for Collapse Syndrome patients, but since it's my first day, I have no clue how to use the patient management app.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row51146009_Aside_AboutRole146: [Celestia lifts a bag filled with bread, cakes, cookies, and a bouquet of flowers peeking out.]
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204060_Aside_AboutRole146: (Still affected by the nostalgic atmosphere of the movie, Celestia sits there, blinking blankly.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203079_Aside_AboutRole146: (Her heartfelt words, though softly spoken, resonate genuinely with everyone present.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202034_Aside_AboutRole146: (Holding her forehead, Celestia suddenly sways, her body tilting, nearly falling down.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204030_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia rushes off before finishing her sentence. I find our reserved seats and sit down.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201028_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia's palm is sweaty—she must've rushed over right after I called.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201036_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia's emergency intervention worked, and the patient has gradually calmed down.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101047_Aside_AboutRole146: (Before Celestia finishes her sentence,  a "boom" startles her.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203029_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia shows me one of the bracelet's crystals, its backside engraved with her name in a child's handwriting.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201040_Aside_AboutRole146: (As Celestia tells me the name of the song, the patient lifts up his head, his eyes filled with longing.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202072_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia gently takes the telescope from my hand and starts adjusting it.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101038_Aside_AboutRole146: (I give Celestia a look filled with determination.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101044_Aside_AboutRole146: (Arriving at the beach, we find a large crowd.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146203055_Aside_AboutRole146: (Patients from diverse backgrounds, ages, and statuses are here. Celestia greets each of them proficiently.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202002_Aside_AboutRole146: (Upon arriving at Astral Sanctuary for work, I hear someone—no, something—calling for Celestia at the entrance.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204085_Aside_AboutRole146: (As instructed by Celestia, I “light” the sparkler.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204003_Aside_AboutRole146: (Cheers, shouts, and clamors accompany the roar of war machines, echoing in Celestia's and my ears.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201074_Aside_AboutRole146: (The singing is neither moving nor unpleasant. Average at best.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201066_Aside_AboutRole146: (Her singing is neither moving nor unpleasant. Average at best.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202026_Aside_AboutRole146: (Celestia is taking a nap, looking more exhausted than usual.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201153_Aside_AboutRole146: (After tapping the Star Pad, only the right side of the screen lit up.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201065_Aside_AboutRole146: (I used the half-broken Star Pad to look up the lyrics and guided Celestia as she sang to the patient.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204086_Aside_AboutRole146: (The sparkler's white light illuminates our faces as our eyes lock.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204055_Aside_AboutRole146: (The opening scene shows columns of tanks advancing under a purple sunset, gunfire tearing through the quiet night.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101028_Aside_AboutRole146: (I glance over Celestia’s shoulder at the computer displaying a map of the area around Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202012_Aside_AboutRole146: (After seeing the bot off, I carry the package into Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202050_Aside_AboutRole146: (Seeing Celestia recover her strength, I start my own work, feeling relieved.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202103_Aside_AboutRole146: (Seeing Celestia’s joy as she adjusts the telescope puts my mind at ease.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202005_Aside_AboutRole146: (After confirming that the packaging is intact, I accept the package from the delivery robot.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201002_Aside_AboutRole146: (On my first day commuting to Astral Sanctuary, I suddenly got caught up with someone sitting dejectedly by the plaza fountain.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101018_Aside_AboutRole146: (Seeing Celestia this defeated for the first time, I have no clue how to comfort her.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101004_Aside_AboutRole146: (A brief message that radiates Celestia's carefree excitement, with a hint of playfulness.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101041_Aside_AboutRole146: (We urgently contact the participants and leave a notice of the change of venue on the electronic noticeboard at Astral Sanctuary.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204018_Aside_AboutRole146: (Even though they’re quite old, they still function well enough to show clear images in daylight.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146202048_Aside_AboutRole146: (After calming Celestia down, I continue to receive visitors.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101002_Aside_AboutRole146: (It's been a week since the movie festival, I receive a text message from Celestia.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146204008_Aside_AboutRole146: (In the setting sun, soldiers lay down their weapons and children return to their homes.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146201073_Aside_AboutRole146: (I went ahead and sang the song to the patient.)
AVGEvent_XingHui.Row146101042_Aside_AboutRole146: (Holding hands, Celestia and I rush to Grand Beach.)

BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row19_PlayerOption1: An event ticket with a butterfly sign?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId115: To ensure your safety, please follow my instructions at every step of the way.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row21_TextContent_FromRoleId115: There is no more free information from now on.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId115: Take a close look at the bottom of the mug...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId115: We'll talk more about it in person.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId115: Go sit in the second to last seat by the window.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId115: If you can defeat me in the event ticket game...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row8_PlayerOption1: I'm here... this must be “Café Reminiscence”.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId115: I've received intel that suggests someone is onto you, Navigator.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row14_PlayerOption1: I ordered a cup of coffee.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row23_TextContent_FromRoleId115: Maybe I can reveal something that you don't know.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId115: Can we meet in private? There's something I need to talk to you about...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId115: See the butterflies outside? Follow them.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId115: Unfortunately, the person who's after you showed up as well.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId115: Hang on. A waiter will bring you a cup of coffee.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row16_PlayerOption1: Oh right... is coffee really all I need?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row19_PlayerOption2: Does this have anything to do with the person after me?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row14_PlayerOption2: Let's try one of their signature drinks.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_1.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId115: Anything will do. Maybe we can get a drink.

BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row21_TextContent_FromRoleId133: ...Yes, after leaving the café, you displayed three significant signs of fatigue and five instances of moderate attention deficit.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Rather than divination, it's more like deduction. I've made it a habit of mine.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Having ordered espresso con panna and mocha, you kept winning.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row30_TextContent_FromRoleId133: From now on, I need to stay close to the guests... Yes, I have to observe closely and take notes...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row28_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Could you please cooperate with me to ensure the accuracy of the data?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId133: But these “coincidences” all seem very similar.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row20_TextContent_FromRoleId133: You're like a fish out of water. Without coffee, you can barely stand up straight.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Your performance in the challenge has close and subtle ties to coffee.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row26_TextContent_FromRoleId133: You just need a lighter dose.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row27_TextContent_FromRoleId133: It only takes a dozen percentage adjustments to get the balance between dependence and health just right.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId133: I have become accustomed to observing and deducing over a long time.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId133: I won three matches in a row after ordering a cup of latte.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Dear guest, I am the manager.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Yes... You've ordered five cups of coffee today.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Just like your preference for coffee.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row23_PlayerOption1: Am I that addicted to caffeine?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row23_PlayerOption2: I might have to think about giving up coffee.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row24_TextContent_FromRoleId133: No need to worry. Drinking coffee is an elegant hobby.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row15_PlayerOption1: Sure enough... But how did you do it?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId133: You just so happened to not order any coffee for this round.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row11_PlayerOption2: I didn't order coffee every time I lost... Is that it?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row25_TextContent_FromRoleId133: That's not necessary. I'm not asking you to give up your hobby.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row19_TextContent_FromRoleId133: Unfamiliarity often leads to discomfort and emotional distance.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row11_PlayerOption1: If you put it this way...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row8_PlayerOption1: This... must be a coincidence, right?
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId133: This record also serves as supporting evidence.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId133: In that case... you can verify it for yourself, my guest.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_2.Row15_PlayerOption2: Don't tell me you can predict the future?

BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId112: It won't take long to clean everything.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId112: I'm just glad you weren't hurt.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row19_PlayerOption2: It's fine even if it's a little later today.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row20_TextContent_FromRoleId112: So... my manager just informed me that the café will continue operations as usual.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId112: The dagger and gun... we'll just consider them prepared for you.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId112: Maids and mercenaries do similar work. It's all about clearing away the “garbage”.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row23_TextContent_FromRoleId112: I hope you've learned your lesson. Next time...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row2_TextContent_FromRoleId112: I went to the café for maid training.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row19_PlayerOption1: I've already spoken to the shopkeeper.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row14_PlayerOption2: I wasn't kidnapped. I'm very safe right now.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row18_TextContent_FromRoleId112: You won't be able to see the results of my maid training...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId112: My Sawtooth and dagger are in their best shapes...
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId112: Since you've already reserved a seat, you should come check out my progress.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId112: What a pity. The café is about to close.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId112: Report your coordinates as soon as possible.
BeautyStyle_335_Lv_3.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId112: And the amount of “trash” you need to clear.

Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row2_PlayerOption1: It might not be over yet.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId101: But everyone left in such a hurry. Especially you, partner... You were the first to go!
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId101: You mean this thing? Mighty Meow just found it on my doorstep...
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row13_PlayerOption2: Everyone's written their thoughts on it...
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Okay, okay, I'll let you be. I'm just going to keep up the spring cleaning...
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I was originally going to ask you to play with me.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row6_PlayerOption2: I've got more important things to do right now.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row1_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I really don't want this birthday party to end.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId101: If it wasn't for you, I wouldn't have received so many birthday wishes! This is the best birthday ever!
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId101: Ehhh? So mysterious... I can't tell what you're thinking at all...
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row9_PlayerOption2: That special someone is about to get a big surprise!
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row13_PlayerOption1: This is something we all worked on together.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_1.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId101: In this way, even after my birthday ends, I'll still feel that everyone is by my side.

Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row2_PlayerOption1: It might not be over yet.
Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId101: But everyone left in such a hurry. Especially you, partner... You were the first to go!
Birthday_Michele_Lv_2.Row1_TextContent_FromRoleId101: I really don't want this birthday party to end.

CinematicCloister.6_Describe: The Navigator and Astierred arrive at the Urbino Business Alliance headquarters, seeking an audience with the mysterious Mr. Bai. An unexpected encounter and an unforeseen covenant await them.
CinematicCloister.17_Describe: In an inconspicuous alley of the Urbino Business Alliance, a song of butterflies and flowers is played.
CinematicCloister.18_Describe:
Stepping away from the stage, follow the shadows to the destination.
Tonight, the grandest flame shall be lit.
CinematicCloister.3_Describe: The Scissors split up in an attempt to seize the crystals amidst the chaos, leading to a confrontation between the two sides.
CinematicCloister.1_Describe: The Scissors team infiltrates Komos Tower to steal the high-purity crystals being refined by P.U.S in order to open a spatial rift.
CinematicCloister.4_Describe: The Scissors successfully obtain the crystals. Having realized The Scissors' plan, P.U.S forces arrive at the location to provide support...
CinematicCloister.16_Describe:
Searching for the shattered truth amidst a fragile situation.
Know this: words are mightier than swords.
CinematicCloister.13_Describe:
The business world is no different from a battlefield. For Audrey in her current situation, this is especially true.
In the aftermath, another war is about to begin.
CinematicCloister.5_Describe: As a result of The Scissors' Operation Crimson Blade, Komos Tower of Area 88, Neutroville, is all but destroyed. Amidst the ensuing chaos, multiple explosions have taken place across the realm. Astral Sanctuary is fully committed to treating the wounded. However, an unexpected change serves as an omen for a more devastating incident.
CinematicCloister.8_Describe: Back at the Sentinel Bureau headquarters, Kokona informs the others of unsettling news. The Navigator works with the Sentinel Bureau to counter the threat to Neutroville and uncover the enemy's hidden identity...
CinematicCloister.21_Describe:
As the dust settles, Audrey honors her promise at Astral Sanctuary.
However... where there is light, there are shadows.
CinematicCloister.9_Describe: While the Navigator is at the Sentinel Bureau, Grove Bank is violently attacked, revealing the identity of the mastermind behind everything. All by herself, Audrey forges a path to victory with blazing flames.
CinematicCloister.7_Describe: As security consultants of the Grove Corporation, the Navigator and Astierred prepare to collaborate with the local Sentinel Bureau of PUS. At the designated meeting place, the duo meets a vibrant new investigator. Unbeknownst to them, the newly formed squad is about to face a severe situation...
CinematicCloister.20_Describe:
We promised her that we'd save every patient.
The dawn only comes when we have endured the deepest darkness.
CinematicCloister.2_Describe: Lawine infiltrates the defense system of Komos Tower alone with the support of The Scissors team. Unexpectedly, the defense system is suddenly being updated...
CinematicCloister.14_Describe:
The heavy rain covers the windows of the Grove mansion as if it were liquid curtains.
A diary and a mail... unveil past hurt.
CinematicCloister.12_Describe:
In an unknown place at an unknown time.
The hunter and the prey face off against each other.
CinematicCloister.10_Describe: In the vault of Grove Bank, the Navigator's team faces a mysterious enemy, setting the stage for the final showdown. On the other side, the surrounded Audrey receives the most unexpected assistance...
CinematicCloister.15_Describe:
Hiding beneath the water, the malice begins to show its face.
Can you distinguish black from white on the chessboard?
CinematicCloister.19_Describe:
A crimson hunter and a flaming unicorn.
As two formidable opponents fight for their lives, who shall emerge victorious...

Emote.60000097_Desc: "No, no, just a little bit more."
Emote.60000080_Desc: “Oh no. It's a new barbecue stall! I'll have to try it now!”
Emote.60001004_Desc: “Are you interested in flowers as well?”
Emote.60000056_Desc: “Do you know what the world inside a donut is like?”
Emote.60000082_Desc: “Can you blow bubbles better than I can?”
Emote.60001014_Desc: “I was so shocked I snapped by paintbrush!”
Emote.60001012_Desc: “I'm not talking to you for the next three minutes!”
Emote.60000092_Desc: “Ha-ha-ha-ha! Amazing! Yes, that. Could you do it again?”
Emote.60001018_Desc: “I feel dizzy. I can't possibly finish all the drafts...”
Emote.60001015_Desc: “Yay! I finished it before the deadline!”
Emote.60000053_Desc: “The 1 Bamboo is a minor mahjong tile, but you need it to win.”
Emote.60000081_Desc: “May the world be full of colors.”
Emote.60000078_Desc: “The way I fell was pretty cool, right?”
Emote.60000087_Desc: “I've been looking forward to this day.”
Emote.60001016_Desc: “My mood is as sweet as a refreshing glass of juice.”
Emote.60000071_Desc: “If I get serious, Mighty Meow won't be the only thing I throw!”
Emote.60000088_Desc: “I'm sorry... I've apologized. You're not mad anymore, are you?”
Emote.60000086_Desc: “How dare you show yourself in Preton? I'll make it pay!”
Emote.60001006_Desc: “Don't worry about me. I just need a moment...”
Emote.60000012_Desc: “I'm off to bed... We'll talk tomorrow.”
Emote.60000067_Desc: “The mysterious power is in your hands.”
Emote.60000057_Desc: “Fay made this glass of milk tea.”
Emote.60000091_Desc: “The Masked Hero would never agree to this!”
Emote.60000075_Desc: “Take a wrong turn, and you may never be able to return.”
Emote.60000094_Desc: “The limited-edition biting shark toy... is sold out?”
Emote.60000093_Desc: “Taiyaki, sweet shark - anything will do. Please!”
Emote.60000118_Desc: Very well, let's have some tea.
Emote.60000116_Desc: Be quiet and follow my lead.
Emote.60000059_Desc: “I'm taking a nap as soon as I'm done eating.”
Emote.60000114_Desc: “To think, or not to think, that is the question...”
Emote.60000084_Desc: “Looks like someone needs to be taught a lesson.”
Emote.60000115_Desc: “Please make me feel better with flowers...”

“Do you have to arrive early for performances? Fine, let's rehearse.” - The Big Bad Wolf, an unemployed person who wishes to remain anonymous
(Opening it 40 times guarantees a perfect character outfit or weapon skin. Opening it 80 times guarantees a full set of perfect character outfits or weapon skins)
Goods.10106111_Desc:
The special edition "Spring Blessing" of "Polaris," inspired by the motif "Ascendance," embodies the courage and determination Celestia has gradually built up through past hardships.

“For the patients, I won't back down anymore. This is what my predecessors taught me.”
Goods.10106108_Desc:
A special customized version of the Polaris featuring a smoothed barrel that provides better grip. The embellished azure crystals also serve as an energy source for the firearm, enabling its bullets to race toward the targets like shooting stars.

【“This is no ordinary wishing star. It always flies toward my desired target.”】
Goods.10106107_Desc:
A custom version of the Polaris, this model loses the original's cold weapon vibe, making it perfect for date nights. The scope also serves as a makeup mirror, enabling users to check their makeup anytime, anywhere.

"That was such a blast! I need to touch up my makeup... Heh.”
Goods.10106106_Desc:
Specialized Polaris model. This firearm was a gift obtained from the Space Expericenter in Polaris. Designed in the shape of a space station, it tells the tale of mankind's longing for the endless expanse. It's not exaggeration to say this firearm is industrial art made manifest.

【“For an endless sky, I offer my endless yearning.”】
Goods.10106201_Desc: A customized version of the "Polaris." The red rose across the barrel symbolizes the fearsome sword of a knight in an ancient tale of heroism.
Goods.10106202_Desc: A customized version of the "Polaris." The red rose across the barrel symbolizes the fearsome sword of a knight in an ancient tale of heroism.
Goods.10106203_Desc: A customized version of the "Polaris." The red rose across the barrel symbolizes the fearsome sword of a knight in an ancient tale of heroism.

Goods.10106105_Desc:
The "Polaris" custom model cleverly incorporates medical themes, seemingly implying anti-war ideals...

They save lives not in the hope of praise, nor do they raise their guns to fight.
In front of them lies war, and behind them, peace.
Goods.10106104_Desc:
Artistic Polaris model. References to fairy tales from old Earth reveal a surprising innocence in this weapon's designer.

【Wrapped in fragile dreams, a child's innocence beams. Kindness and purity, in our essence, gleams.】
Goods.10403108_Desc:
A customized version of the "Champion" featuring enhanced sensitivity to light. Whether for photography or firing bullets, it performs in perfection.

“This moment is worth capturing, don't you think?”
Goods.10403201_Desc:
A personalized "Champion" model with a pristine barrel, basking in the Grove family's glory and victories. Fervent flames flow through it, symbolizing Lord Grove's indomitable spirit.

To protect her family, the young girl took this gun onto the battlefield. Now, with the newly upgraded weapon in hand, there's composure and determination in her once-furrowed brow. The answers to those questions? As before, seek them through bullets.
Goods.10403106_Desc: A customized artistic version of the "Champion," adorned with strings of the Guqin, concealing the pinnacle of technology under the classic design.
Goods.10403104_Desc:
The custom "Champion" design by Audrey incorporates four unique musical elements. Each string of notes plays the same melody with distinct tones.

"It's a piano, a saxophone, an old vinyl spinning in solitude, capturing the faded memories of the past. I don't know what eras this gun has witnessed, but the moment it fires, the past becomes crystal clear."
Goods.10403105_Desc: The artistic custom version of "Champion" is inspired by old Earth's local folklore, vividly showcasing a deeply cultural aesthetic.
Goods.31000184_Desc: “As her deformed body falls into eternal decay, she draws the corrupted souls into the sea of flowers nevertheless.”
Goods.10111005_Desc: The "Rebel" series features a striking color contrast and a pattern design resembling a swift, powerful lightning bolt, perfectly capturing the spirit of rebellion and defiance.
Goods.31000193_Desc: “Silent is the ancient temple, yet the footsteps of pioneers and successors echo throughout.”
Goods.60001014_Desc: “I was so shocked I snapped by paintbrush!”
Goods.60001012_Desc: “I'm not talking to you for the next three minutes!”
Goods.60000092_Desc: “Ha-ha-ha-ha! Amazing! Yes, that. Could you do it again?”
Goods.31000154_Desc:
“Meow! Meow, meow, meow!”
Pawtector seems to be training Mighty Meow, who is not so good at video games.
Goods.10106003_Desc: The "Multiverse" series features a Strinova-inspired design. Its simple yet intricate patterns exude a unique charm.
Goods.10108003_Desc: The "Multiverse" series features a Strinova-inspired design. Its simple yet intricate patterns exude a unique charm.

Goods.60001018_Desc: “I feel dizzy. I can't possibly finish all the drafts...”
Goods.60001015_Desc: “Yay! I finished it before the deadline!”
Goods.31000186_Desc: “She... It stands on top of the tower, bringing down endless fear and confusion.”
Goods.31000185_Desc: “If you find it, please listen carefully. What's sealed is not a mad desire but a trembling heart.”
Goods.31001065_Desc: “Please let us know if anything is not to your liking.”
Goods.10304105_Desc:
The custom "Judge" design is ideal for use by the water. The hovercraft-shaped barrel stabilizes the gun, enhancing its performance.

"I've spent too long thinking; it's time to enter the battlefield. There's still a long journey to my objective."
Goods.10304103_Desc:
A customized version of the Judge. Under the setting sun, two cranes fly away, bidding farewell to the departed.

【The wings of the crane shall guide you home.】
Goods.10304102_Desc:
The custom "Judge" concept features a cyberpunk theme with a stylish color palette. It's vibrant yet thought-provoking.

"Neon lights haven't yet faded, and dawn remains uncertain. Though the glory of the past remains, under the clashing of steel, the light of civilization no longer shines."
Goods.10304108_Desc:
A modified version of the "Judge" that incorporates chess pieces into the design, exclusively customized for chess show matches. Its sleek black and gold design makes it one of Nobunaga's favorites.

"I'll always be one move ahead of you."
Goods.10304109_Desc:
A modified version of the Judge that incorporates chess pieces into the design, exclusively customized for chess show matches. Its sleek black and gold design makes it one of Nobunaga's favorites.

【"I will also think one move ahead of you."】
Goods.10403107_Desc:
The customized “Manor's Grace” model showcases intricate design and elegant drum, proving that high art can be just as deadly.

“Today's menu includes refreshing tea, delicious snacks, and a hearty supply of bullets.”
Goods.31001066_Desc: “I'll come visit often, if only for the amazing tea.”
Goods.10106006_Desc: The "Chimera" series features an elegant orange mosaic design with deep and light tones, creating an artistic look.
Goods.10108006_Desc: The "Chimera" series features an elegant orange mosaic design with deep and light tones, creating an artistic look.
Goods.10301006_Desc: The "Chimera" series features an elegant orange mosaic design with deep and light tones, creating an artistic look.

Goods.60000053_Desc: “The 1 Bamboo is a minor mahjong tile, but you need it to win.”
Goods.10501103_Desc:
The personalized "Beareas" model features a luxurious purple finish, a cute panda face, and a fierce soundwave effect when firing, symbolizing the passionate heart hidden beneath the user’s cold exterior.

“The taciturn girl pursed her lips tightly, letting out no sound. The music dancing with gunfire speaks for her.”
Goods.10501104_Desc:
The custom "Beareas" design was hazily sketched by Yvette after a ten-hour sugar crash.

"My hands just... did their thing! Not that I was itching to try the new model or anything."
Goods.10501111_Desc:
The special medical edition of "Beareas" features syringe and tube elements, monitoring opponents' heartbeats in real-time.

“Please... open up to me.”
Goods.10501102_Desc:
The custom "Beareas" model trades its icy look for a corn-themed design symbolizing life and harvest. It's hard not to find it... a bit appetizing.

"Uh... I know you're hungry, but this isn't for making popcorn..."
Goods.10501109_Desc:
A special edition "Beareas" model, featuring a bold retro-artistic design. Inspired by luminous pearls, it’s set with these gems, giving it an extraordinary elegance.

"The pearl in your hand sparkles, dazzling ever more gloriously in the dark."
Goods.10501201_Desc:
A special ball edition of "Beareas" is more compact and lightweight, with added mechanical and gear elements, seamlessly complementing an evening gown.

“I know I'm going to a ball, but I want to bring Fay and my gun... Otherwise, I may feel insecure...”
Goods.10101003_Desc: From the "Colorburst" series. Painted with streaks of different pigments. This firearm has a casual vibe, but it's overflowing with artistic flair.
Goods.10202003_Desc: From the "Colorburst" series. Painted with streaks of different pigments. This firearm has a casual vibe, but it's overflowing with artistic flair.
Goods.10304003_Desc: From the "Colorburst" series. Painted with streaks of different pigments. This firearm has a casual vibe, but it's overflowing with artistic flair.
Goods.10501005_Desc: From the "Colorburst" series. Painted with streaks of different pigments. This firearm has a casual vibe, but it's overflowing with artistic flair.
Goods.10502005_Desc: From the "Colorburst" series. Painted with streaks of different pigments. This firearm has a casual vibe, but it's overflowing with artistic flair.
Goods.10301105_Desc:
A customized "Chroma" model, ideal for outdoor combat. The gun's decor is inspired by animals Maddelena sketched in the wild, with cute expressions sure to bring a smile.

"This is my little companion. Why not say hello?"
Goods.10301104_Desc:
The "Chroma" custom model features a cute water gun design. When it fires, the bullets surge like raging waves.

"The sea can be calm, yet it can also swallow everything. Freedom is similar; pursuing it might bring happiness or destruction."
Goods.10301106_Desc:
The customized "Chroma" features a sleek space design enhanced with pink-purple energy beams symbolizing cosmic nebulae. These beams not only provide powerful energy for the weapon but also serve as excellent illuminators, making her creation shine brightly in the dark void of space.

“Let me adorn you to make you even more radiant.”
Goods.10301111_Desc:
Specialized Chroma model. Adorned in bright green and decorated with cartoonish characters, this firearm is the perfect embodiment of Maddelena - romantic whimsy and childlike innocence.

【“It's funny, isn't it? When we're young, we couldn't wait to grow up, and now that we're grown, we wish we could be children again.'"】
Goods.10301102_Desc:
A customized concept model of the "Chroma." Inspired by Maddalena's aesthetics, it features her favorite bunny-themed elements.

"The last bunny rides a rocket into the depths of space.
In the vastness of stars, a spark rises into the unknown, marking the end of the glorious bunny civilization."
Goods.10301110_Desc:
Specialized Chroma model. Adorned in bright green and decorated with cartoonish characters, this firearm is the perfect embodiment of Maddelena - romantic whimsy and childlike innocence.

【“It's funny, isn't it? When you're young, I couldn't wait to grow up. But now, I just want to be a kid again.”】
Goods.10301107_Desc:
A lightweight modification of the Chroma featuring a design that incorporates an impressionistic approach to the concept of melody. When you fire it, the sound of gunfire becomes lively musical notes.

【“It's time to dance, my friends!”】
Goods.10104110_Desc:
A customized "Shadow Assault" model, featuring a sapphire seamlessly set into the hollow barrel, mirroring The Scissors' flawless plan.

"It's time!"
Goods.10104107_Desc:
A customized version of the Shadow Assault featuring clever camouflage suitable for convert operations, embodying the concept of patience.

【“Hey, are the leaves talking?”】
Goods.10104113_Desc:
A special underground bar edition of the "Shadow Assault," decorated with intricately carved orchids. While most people consider orchids fragile and fragrant, Lawine believes they represent purity and steadfastness.

"If they had a scent, it’d be a cold one."
Goods.10104101_Desc:
The customized "Shadow Assault" features gilded edges like the setting sun and a crimson barrel resembling twilight clouds, symbolizing the splendid future people once hoped to see.

“Beautiful as the evening glow may be, it cannot escape the storm that cleanses the sky.”
Goods.10104106_Desc:
Customized Shadow Assault model. Though the signature PUS blue and white color scheme may imply otherwise, this weapon was created by Quadrant Foundries.

【Ridding myself of falsehoods has allowed me to become who I am now.
No more needs to be said. One just needs to seek.】
Goods.10104201_Desc:
A personalized "Shadow Assault" model, featuring plum blossom motifs and classical elements. It embodies legendary heroism and enduring pride, ready to confront any battle alongside its master.

"As snow falls in the dark, the battlefield is wrapped in a frigid embrace. As comrades fell, a lone general stood firm against the gale and snow. The sudden storm buried everything—including, perhaps, the plum tree. Yet, as a leader, the general remained unyielding, determined to keep her promise beneath the plum blossom.

Surely, once winter passes, the arrival of spring is not far behind."
Goods.10104112_Desc:
A camouflage edition of the Shadow Assault, painted by Reiichi to aid stealth in the wilderness. As Lawine and her gun blend in with the earth, ryegrass, wild oats, and countless plants she cannot name sway as she crawls forward.

"Even wild grass has its own charm. Its roots are deep and unyielding."
Goods.10501106_Desc:
The customized "Frost Core" model features a delicate ice core encased in intricate metalwork. The bullets it fires are not scorching hot, but bone-chillingly cold.

“Rest assured, this bullet won't hurt you, but it may harm you in another way.”
Goods.60000081_Desc: “May the world be full of colors.”
Goods.31000189_Desc: “We had the purest intentions, but the tower eventually led to opposite ends.”
Goods.60000078_Desc: “The way I fell was pretty cool, right?”
Goods.60000087_Desc: “I've been looking forward to this day.”
Goods.60001016_Desc: “My mood is as sweet as a refreshing glass of juice.”
Goods.60000071_Desc: “If I get serious, Mighty Meow won't be the only thing I throw!”
Goods.20107206_Desc:
"The most important ability of a detective is..."
"What is it?"
"Uh... Observing, summarizing, analyzing, and putting it into practice!"
"That's it? I expected some secrets. Don't forget you promised to catch the thief first."
"When is the thief planning to strike?"
"...Now."
"Oh! I better not waste time here! I'm off to find clues. See you!"

A girl with a coffee cup flits from a steam engine to an ancient whale fossil, exploring mischievously. In the retro museum, a battle between detective and thief is about to begin.
"I shouldn't have taken this job. I have no experience with thieves..." The detective nervously sips her coffee.
Her frustration centers around the exhibit in the glass case before her: the "Icarus Device." This legendary gadget, crafted with retro steam technology, uses intricate mechanisms to let a person fly—useless to Maddalena, but perfect for her quirky collection.
A notorious thief has issued a warning, vowing to snatch the Icarus Device in plain sight. Due to the bustling shopping festival, the warning arrives at the museum just a day before the scheduled heist. Desperate, the curator calls Urbino for help.
To cover her coffee expenses for the next month and the maintenance for her Fully Automatic Creative Retro Victorian Steampunk Gothic Hand-Operated Mechanical Latte Mocha Espresso Flat White Compression Modulating Machine, Maddalena jumps into action.
However...

“Welcome to The Hometown. How would you like your egg cooked?”
Shows like this seem to be quite popular at the restaurant called The Hometown.
Goods.10112102_Desc:
A special pool party edition of the "Trickster." Inspired by seashells, the streamlined design features colors of seawater, beaches, and hibiscus, exuding a retro, romantic feeling.

"Before you play the next song, grab a drink at the bar. The night is still young."
Goods.20112111_Desc:
The realm of martial arts is supreme and pure. For a martial artist to break through in technique, they must first break through their mindset. Fuchsia does not entirely agree, but she secretly hopes to find the answers someday.

“What are martial arts? Why do we practice them? Are the answers really that important? I never cared about these questions, and look how far I've come.”
Goods.20120051_Desc:
"Each type of coffee bean has a unique aroma." Fragrans places the cup of coffee in front of Eika. "This one has floral and fruity notes. It should be delightful."

"Really? Like, as sweet as fruit?... Ah! It's so sour!!!"
Goods.60001006_Desc: “Don't worry about me. I just need a moment...”
Goods.10102003_Desc: The "Tidal Wave" series is composed of a series of blue modules meant to imitate the shape of a wave. It may lack the sound of the sea, but it remains a delight.

【Kong! Kong! Kong! Kong and calling a win! Great winds! All kongs!】

“You almost hit Captain Michele!”

“You will beg for mercy.”

“The pinker the skin, the stronger the blow.”

Michele smiles brightly as she wipes the sweat from her brow.

【Researchers at Polaris Labs were initially reluctant at the thought anyone could safely wield so much string energy when Michele submitted her original proposal.
“You're talking to Michele·Lee! I can handle anything, even a black hole!”】
Goods.10101202_Desc:
The custom Inspector showcases a white tiger emblem on its dark barrel, with blue Energy flowing throughout the gun. Its wielder charges to the frontlines of justice with unwavering resolve.

When Michele submitted her modification request, the researchers at Polaris Labs were taken aback, doubting anyone could handle such wild string energy.

A customized version of the Rebelflame featuring a pale blue paint job with plenty of silver ornaments. Each shot is accompanied by the pleasant ringing of a bell as if it were telling an ancient legend.

【Huh? No need for those clichéd stories. I'll write my own legend.】

A customized "Rebelflame," blending the sharpness of an eagle with the free spirit of a cowboy, perfectly captures a maverick's bravery and fearlessness.

"No prey seen by this eagle will ever escape."

A customized model of the Rebelflame, with a thunderbolt-shaped barrel through which electricity surges like a dragon. Its gunshot is as loud as its owner's reputation. Rumor has it that a single shot from this weapon shakes the land like thunder, echoing through the world.

The Scissors' long-standing tradition of welcoming newcomers with stories has evolved into a martial arts showcase, drawing listeners from all over. As the vice-captain and speaker for the assault team, he eagerly shares tales of the captain's exploits.
During one session, while recounting the Wasteland Thunder story for the 50th time, a young listener unexpectedly interrupts, requesting to hear the adventures of the Thunderous Dragon outsmarting criminals.
Just as he prepares to answer, a figure in a battle suit makes a dramatic entrance.
“P-Prepare for combat? Now? What's the mission, Captain?”
“Simply put, it's a battle of wits against criminals!”
After grabbing a bag of chips, the figure waves to the young listener.
“Seeing is believing! Today, you'll witness it firsthand!”
Goods.31000180_Desc: “Youth, courage, a world to explore. We had everything, our hope undying.”

But now,
the gilded masks remain elegant; the ancient power as strong as ever,
a shimmering brilliance from a distant past.】

A customized "Wildfire" with Eika's favorite space elements and a special flame-simulation device. After all, her dream is to be the coolest, most fired-up courier in the universe.

"Who would have thought that a little spark could light up the entire universe?"
Goods.10603103_Desc:
The "Wildfire" deep sea edition is inspired by Eika's favorite fish, featuring vibrant patterns that shine as brightly as Eika's sparks.

"Fiery Fish in blazing orange, making a grand entrance!"
Goods.10603101_Desc:
The design of "Wildfire" draws inspiration from the latest high school fashion trends. Flames shooting from the barrel symbolize youthful energy.

"Woo! Fire it up!"
Goods.10108112_Desc:
The modified "Sawtooth" has been by Fuchsia's side since childhood. Its cold barrel holds warmth in her heart.

"The path to mastery is not one I walk alone."
Goods.10108201_Desc:
A customized edition of the Sawtooth, inspired by the skeleton of a shark from old Earth. Equipped with high-performance light elements, recreating the might and solitude of the deep-sea beast.

Strinova's marine ecosystem is broken. Among the ocean's migratory creatures, only the sharks survived. Yet, they have lost their sharpness and strength, and even their sense of smell is fading. Bionic technology was needed to restore their former glory.
When Fuchsia received the modified Sawtooth, she couldn't help but admire the exquisite attention to detail.
“No big deal. It's only a scaled replica of a shark skeleton salvaged from the deep sea.”
The gunsmith remarks with a nonchalant raise of his eyebrow.
“The deep sea? Are there still sharks out there?
“Sadly, there remains just one... My colleague from Bionic Tech mentioned it's been extremely agitated lately."
Sharks are typically solitary and composed, so why this sudden agitation? Fuchsia is eager to uncover the reason behind the shark's unusual behavior.
Goods.10108109_Desc:
Custom Sawtooth model. Lightweight yet powerful, it works like a vacuum to efficiently clear away any unwanted 'trash and debris'.

[Cleaning like a maid, but with bullets.]
Goods.10108104_Desc:
The "Sawtooth" concept custom model draws inspiration from ancient hunters. In times past, people feared those nocturnal stalkers, never knowing if they were the next target.

"In complete silence, she delivers an unpredictable fate."
Goods.10108107_Desc:
A camo-modified version of "Sawtooth." Beyond its camouflage design, it features bionic technology... What's it for? Maybe it even helps repel mosquitoes.

"Thanks to it, I no longer have to worry about getting mosquito bites while in hiding."
Goods.10102055_Desc: The "Lion Dance" series features a festive yellow and white design, depicting Scissors members performing lion dances, embodying spirit and vitality.
Goods.10104055_Desc: The "Lion Dance" series features a festive yellow and white design, depicting Scissors members performing lion dances, embodying spirit and vitality.
