Goods.10303055_Desc: The "Lion Dance" series features a festive yellow and white design, depicting Scissors members performing lion dances, embodying spirit and vitality.
Goods.10603054_Desc: The "Lion Dance" series features a festive yellow and white design, depicting Scissors members performing lion dances, embodying spirit and vitality.
Goods.10603105_Desc:
A special medical model of "Wildfire." Its bullets are cleverly shaped like pills to appear less threatening. That's the hope, anyway.

"We'll have to add 'gunshot wound' to your medical history."
Goods.10603106_Desc:
A desert edition of "Wildfire," rumored to grant three wishes. Yet, its current owner chooses to reach her goals through her own efforts.

“I wish to defeat all my enemies!”
Goods.20110105_Desc:
A modified stealth suit inspired by the movie "Phantom Thief," with a sleek, fitted design that matches Bai Mo's taste for style and comfort. However, the added custom bandages and neon glasses kind of defeat the purpose.

Standing in front of a mirror, Bai Mo marvels at his style, but what happens next is unforgettable - “Hmm, cosplaying as the Phantom Thief once in a while isn't half bad. Hey! Let me go! I'm not a thief!”
Goods.30000118_Desc:
“When the cat tripped over a rock, the snow leopard cub took the opportunity to get a lead!”
This special gift commemorates the first anniversary of Strinova. This item was selected as the best creation of the graffiti creation event. The introduction is provided by the creator.
Goods.31002002_Desc:
“Have you ever truly looked at the starry sky?”
“I heard there is a unique star for everyone, waiting alone in the universe, hoping someone would gaze at it.”
“If one day you see an unusual light in the sky, that's probably your star winking at you.”
“Where is my star? Well... that's a secret.”

The girl never stops chasing the night sky.
Through countless nights under the stars, she patiently waits for that one star in the vast galaxy to reveal itself.
One day, the star winks at her.
And the entire night sky changes its colors.
Goods.31002005_Desc:
【“Whether it's going on an adventure or simply sleeping in, one must do what they love the most on a rare off day!”
Having finished a day's work, Kokona changes into comfortable clothes and lays down.

Next to her are stacks of boxes and all kinds of items.
Among them are memorabilia she has not had time to organize and essential tools for her future explorations.
“Come on. Don't just stand there. Help me out.”】
Goods.31002007_Desc:
“It's not that I don't like going out...”
The girl shyly pulls down the brim of her bear hoodie. “It's just that there are too many people outside, and it's noisy... At home, I have Fay, blankets, and endless chilled drinks...”
“I think it's really nice to just stay at home... W-Wouldn't you agree?”
Goods.31002006_Desc:
【“Today, I have to design a children's book for Astral Sanctuary. As for tomorrow, I promised my neighbor I'd help her design her living room...”
It is another incredibly fulfilling day for the girl who finds joy in helping others. But this time, you notice a hint of weariness in her expression.

“Hold on, Advisor. Don't move!
“That's it! That's the look!”
The girl exclaims as if she has found the world's rarest treasure.
“Since it's your day off... Advisor, would you model for me?”
The girl approaches the person she trusts the most, sharing her unique warmth, her eyes filled with you and only you.】
Goods.31002009_Desc:
【“Would you like another taiyaki? Or a sweet shark?”
Sitting on a floor mat, Fuchsia extends her hands to me, offering a piece of taiyaki in one and a sweet shark in the other - a dilemma of sweetness.
Although it is really tempting, I have already had too many sweet snacks today. I swallow as I firmly refuse Fuchsia's offer.
“Suit yourself.” Fuchsia shrugs before taking a huge bite, licking the crumbs from the corner of her mouth. Then, she stretches lazily and sprawls on the floor.
“This is how you should spend your holiday.”】
Goods.31002004_Desc:
【“What flower is this? It's an orchid.”
The floral fragrance of the tea wafts from the cups in front of Lawine and you.
The pale petals unfold in your cup of tea.
You notice that a similar flower is embroidered on her clothes.

“Orchids only bloom in spring, a season far too short in this world.”
As she sips some tea, the girl in front of you smiles, barely perceptible.
For her, this brief respite from all her responsibilities and duties is her spring.】
Goods.31002003_Desc:
【After playing a violin piece, Audrey sits next to you.
“Why do you still look so gloomy when I'm with you?”
“What are you worried about? The test we have to face? Or the inevitable collapse?”

She pours two cups of black tea and places one in front of you.
“Let go of all the troubles. Let us toast to hardship and... this world.”
As the cups touch, producing a crisp sound, the girl smiles confidently.】
Goods.31002008_Desc:
【As an idol, Kanami enjoys spending time on makeup and styles.
Whether it's a natural look or an elegant stage look, Kanami excels at putting them on, skillfully applying any makeup products.
As Kanami finishes her makeup, she draws a cute mark on the mirror with her lipstick.
“Navigator, will you be colored by my hues?”】
Goods.31002001_Desc:
【As a super gamer, Michele owns many stylish and casual outfits. However, as she is also a cat lady, she prefers this cute cat-themed outfit, whether for its comfort or adorable cat-like colors.

“A cat showing its belly is a sign of being friendly and feeling safe.” The girl says, smiling.

Michele has changed her flashy gamer gear into a cute girl's outfit. Is the cat-like girl trying to tell you something?】
Goods.31001002_Desc:
Having become a frontline investigator, Michele carries with her the will of all her predecessors. When a badge number is reactivated, the pitiful criminals better tremble in fear, for the successor of the White Tiger will defeat every single one of them.

“Listen up! I have you surrounded! Surrender now!” Michele once intimidated suspects like this during operations.
And she kept her word, singlehandedly arresting over a dozen suspects.
"I thought I wouldn't see the light of day again. Was she going to devour us like a wild tiger?" a criminal recalls, trembling in fear.
Goods.31000178_Desc: 【The shark in the tank does not realize its freedom is lost, nor does it feel any pain. People pity it for losing the dignity of a predator, but the shark does not care.】
Goods.31001001_Desc:
The royal swordswoman, enchanting as a rose, gazes into the distance.
She sees nothing but carnage and rivers of blood.
The rose-decorated sword pierces an enemy's heart.
The rose is dyed in blood's hue; shadows cast wide their pall.
Her mind, like the breeze, wanders far, unconfined by any wall.
“For you alone, the flowers unveil their bloom; should they fade, what sorrow calls?”
Goods.30000035_Desc: Alone in the forest, one can only hear the sound of falling bamboo leaves.
Goods.22132079_Desc: All injustice will perish in gunfire!
Goods.31000112_Desc: The start of all joys and sorrows.
Goods.30000106_Desc: Two pumpkins? What a sticky situation.
Goods.20101101_Desc:
A sporty baseball uniform with playful cat ears and a tail. Donning this outfit, Michele seems impressively agile and sharp.

“Steal! Steal! Steal! Base after base!”
As the audience's thunderous cheering fills the stadium, Michele dashes to second base.
Not only is she a super good gamer, Michele is also great at sports.
Her glistening sweat and bright, sunny smile are the most beautiful sight on the field.
Goods.30002051_Desc: A top-notch water gun can turn the tide in any splash battle!
Goods.30000126_Desc: A small gesture of my goodwill.
Goods.22101069_Desc: Fight with me, and justice will be ours!
Goods.30002024_Desc: It's three o'clock! Time for tea!
Goods.30002070_Desc: I won the first half. I'll win the second half, too!
Goods.31000108_Desc: Would you like a cup of tea?
Goods.22115073_Desc: If you want to avoid being charmed, you have to do more than just closing your eyes.
Goods.30000075_Desc: Children who don't want to grow up should never give up their playful nature!
Goods.20133107_Desc:
A mysterious guest has appeared at the underground bar. No one knows what brought her here or what secrets she holds.

"Are you sure we haven't met before? I can't help but feel like I've asked you this exact question many times before."
Goods.22128112_Desc: Do not sink into the darkness!
Goods.22119112_Desc: Don't stop Aika! Is this what it feels like?
Goods.30002008_Desc: From “Hello, world,” code has built it all.
Goods.20109057_Desc: In sharp contrast to Reiichi's indifferent demeanor, this outfit features patterns of raging flames. Even the coldest of tools need to be driven by heat.
Goods.20101105_Desc:
In stark contrast to her usual authoritative demeanor, Michele becomes a mischievous demon straight out of a fairy tale.
 
[Knock, knock. “Open up. It's Investigator Michele from the underworld. I'm here to inspect your snack stash today!”
Donning this outfit, Michele appears happier than usual.
But she's still herself. So, it should be fine, right?]
Goods.20108101_Desc:
Nobunaga's exclusive P.U.S. Spec Ops suit blends steel and leather, yet his elegance and calm demeanor remain undiminished.

“Activate remote control and the radar system. Don’t let anything slip past.”
Under Nobunaga's command, a meticulous raid is underway.
However, the operation ended before it even began.
"You must be the target. So, will you surrender? Or will you make me do it?"
Goods.25006_Name: Exclusive Spring Blessing Selection Gift Box
Goods.31000002_Desc: The anchor of the world. The beacon of the city. A shining tower of string energy.
Goods.22128113_Desc: This world isn't yours to take!
Goods.30002022_Desc: Sweet and homely, like the moonlight.
Goods.20901002_Desc: The question mark displayed on players who join mid-match
Goods.30002023_Desc: Rich and fragrant, with an enduring aftertaste.
Goods.20101051_Desc:
Michele leapt at the chance to customize her own racing outfit for the Port Euler Jet Ski Grand Prix.

Three, two, one... Go!!!
Goods.20131058_Desc: In order to study the impact of letters on people's emotions, Yvette dons the courier's outfit, delivering letters to different households to feel their sentiments. However, when looking at the person she wants to send a letter to, Yvette notices her heartbeat suddenly accelerating.
Goods.30002046_Desc: Why are pets so obsessed with tissues?
Goods.20133053_Desc: A special outfit customized for Meredith with a diamond core symbolizing her sharp, rational, and unwavering resolve.
Goods.20133101_Desc:
While working for P.U.S, Meredith once led a team to explore the True Wilderness. She designed this outfit to embody the spirit of adventure.

“If explorers halt due to the fear of the unknown, it will undermine humanity's courage and future.”
Goods.20109103_Desc:
A special combat suit designed for experimental high-energy electromagnetic weapons, with enhanced insulation based on Reiichi's combat experience.
The silent sniper enters the battlefield, channeling intense energy.

“Careful. You might get a shock.”
Goods.30001012_Desc: My active skill is still in cooldown. Maybe we should pull back for now...
Goods.22109073_Name: Active skill: Light screen, blind them!
Goods.22205073_Name: Active Skill: Another Side of Me
Goods.22120074_Name: Active Skill: Give it a Try
Goods.22108074_Name: Active Skill: Leave It to Me
Goods.60000118_Desc: Very well, let's have some tea.
Goods.20107101_Desc:
It's been said that an explorer who can't fish isn't a true artist.
To visit the remote ecological zones in Strian's countryside for field sketches, Maddelena prepared this outdoor set. She journeys along the river, alternating between sketching and fishing, filling her canvas and fish basket.

"Yes! Got one! Don't run away! Taste my paint bubbles!”
Goods.31000052_Desc: The end of humanity is displayed here in its most unpleasant form.
Goods.31001009_Desc: Today, there will be... a different kind of rain.
Goods.31001004_Desc: Today, we sing! Tomorrow, we fight as one!
Goods.20112051_Desc:
Since when
have we been trapped within the confines of towering steel?
The starry sky grows dim,
no longer illuminating the path arrived on.
Goods.31000005_Desc: Overflowing from the fragments is the color of the soul.
Goods.22137073_Desc: Listen closely, there will be echoes.
Goods.20109105_Desc:
Reiichi's outfit for chess exhibition matches. The fedora and the extra wide lapel add a touch of leisure to the elegance, while the plain glasses provide a unique impression. Together with the dyed hair, one would not recognize him if not a close acquaintance.

“How many times have I told you? The whole point of the Queen's Gambit is to ensure the safety of the central board. Now isn't the time to sweat over a single pawn.”
Goods.20109101_Desc:
Reiichi's outfit for eavesdropping missions.
Blending in is part of being a spy, even in a café.

"Today, there will be... a different kind of rain."
Goods.20109102_Desc:
Reiichi prepared this diving suit while on a seaside vacation. While most of the gadgets on it are functional, it also features some fancy trinkets.

【“Phew... There are many beautiful corals even in the sea.”
As Reiichi emerges from the sea after diving, he shows a faint smile.
The usually indifferent man seems to genuinely enjoy this seaside trip.
“Relax. I'm an easy guy to get along with.”
You feel like you have seen a rare side of Reiichi.】
Goods.20109003_Desc: A variant of Reiichi's combat uniform. Even in total darkness, he harbors a glimmer of hope.
Goods.20109007_Desc: A variant of Reiichi's combat uniform. The army green symbolizes his discipline.
Goods.20109005_Desc:
Reiichi's backup combat suit. Fully functional, its combat capabilities are comparable to the original.

“Do not stop fighting. Do not despair.”
Goods.20109004_Desc: Reiichi's backup combat suit. The deep blue hue sings a song of sorrow.
Goods.20109008_Desc: A variant of Reiichi's combat uniform. The light blue shirt symbolizes the clear sky in his heart.
Goods.20109002_Desc: Reiichi's backup combat suit, with a mysterious purple lining, conceals his many burdens.
Goods.20109009_Desc: A variant of Reiichi's combat uniform. The dim green symbolizes his nearly withered yet undying hope.
Goods.20109010_Desc: A variant of Reiichi's combat uniform. The bright shirt contrasts sharply with the dark coat. He rarely wears it.
Goods.20109104_Desc:
Reiichi's personal outfit, customized based on old space suits. Though partly resembling the original, it has been modified for combat readiness in case of emergency missions. Had there been conflict in the world, perhaps Reiichi would have become an astronaut, scattering his brilliant ideas across the vast universe.

【“Air pressure normal; temperature normal... It's a pity a propulsion device couldn't be fitted.”】
Goods.20109106_Desc:
Reiichi’s special gear for infiltrating the black market emphasizes the mystical allure of Eastern charm and his personal style. The pendant he wears is made from polished scrap, not a genuine antique, but convincing enough to pass as one.

“Heh... You've got a good eye. This is top-notch stuff.”
Goods.10304107_Desc:
One of the pieces of equipment Reiichi has modified. Featuring elements of stage lights and performance cars, it comes with special sound effects that satisfy Reiichi's pursuit of power and speed.

"Every street drummer dreams of performing on the grandest stage."
Goods.10303106_Desc:
One of Reiichi's modified weapons. The firearm's design has been altered to reflect a black market aesthetic. It’s an excellent piece of art—the decorations may be fake, but its lethality is real.

"When true is false, false is true; when false is true, true is false."
Goods.10304104_Desc:
New model based on the "Judge." The hidden Bablo Crystal inside has vastly improved the firearm's performance.

"Why dwell on the past?
Reject the old. Eliminate the stagnant. Destroy the obsolete.
And then... Embrace the new."
Goods.10104105_Desc:
A cyberpunk-style "Shadow Assault" model. Its dark blue barrel emits a violet glow, resembling an impending storm with thunder and lightning concealed among the clouds.

"Fear not every moment."
- The Song of Eternity
Goods.10303101_Desc:
A long-range precision weapon designed based on the Dawn. A masterpiece of Quadrant Foundries, it features significantly improved range and accuracy compared to the original, making it an ace on the battlefield.

【Those hidden in the dark of the night await the light. They gaze at the sky many a times, hoping to find traces in the darkness.
Until a glimmer of light appears in the night sky, lighting the remaining beacons of hope.
Thus, dawn approaches.】
Goods.20128101_Desc:
Inspired by bamboo, this elegant outfit evokes a sense of peace, filled with Lawine's longing for her homeland.

【In her spare time, she often visits her cabin in the bamboo forest.
Through the gaps in the bamboo forest, the sun shines on the dim wooden floor.
Even with you by her side, she remains silent nonetheless.
Quietly, she hands you a fresh cup of tea.】
Goods.10102105_Desc:
Based on the "Rebelflame," Quadrant Foundries introduces a fully updated model. Featuring a silver-gray metal body with a subtle red glow, it radiates a fierce intent.

"Our will is as strong as steel. Together, let's burn the oppressors to ashes."
Goods.10102104_Desc:
Based on the "Rebelflame," this cutting-edge weapon has been redesigned by Quadrant Foundries, enhancing its overall performance while retaining its original form.

"What catalyst drives scientific progress? It's simple: war."
Goods.20131054_Desc: A cute lab coat decorated with clovers. Hope, faith, love, and fortune —Yvette wishes all these good things to be with you.
Goods.20107104_Desc:
A space-themed white bodysuit featuring stylish mecha rabbit ears, making Maddelena seem less simple and more daring than usual.
 
 “Look! Doesn't the reflection of this outfit resemble moonlight?”
 “I heard that a bunny lived happily on the Moon. Could there be a mecha bunny on Strinova's moon as well?”
 The girl happily dreams of space under the cover of the night.
Goods.20105053_Desc: An elegant outfit inspired by playing cards. Hearts, Diamonds, Spades, and Clubs... Where's the Ace? Of course, it's Audrey herself!
Goods.20132206_Desc: Named after the ancient "Lei Loong," this heroic attire features motifs of dragons and crackling lightning. It accompanies its master across lands and seas, becoming a legendary tale among adventurers.

An outfit inspired by cranes, featuring two white cranes painted on a black background as if they are soaring from an inky pine forest, chasing daylight.
Nobunaga always feels nostalgic when he dons this outfit. During the P.U.S Investigator course, he learned ancient Eastern military strategies—"Crane Wing Formation" was once their forte, requiring two partners to flank the enemy from both sides. Even without a partner, Nobunaga has managed to adapt the same tactics for solo combat.

“I have you surrounded. Surrender now.”
Goods.30000102_Desc: There's only one word that comes to mind in defeat - destruction!
Goods.20131206_Desc: Yvette's dress for the P.U.S ball. While she still feels shy about dressing so formally, she finds it nice to show a different side of herself every now and then.

Goods.20131107_Desc:
Yvette's outfit for the Urbino talent show. The light dress evokes poetic scenery of ancient civilizations. Yvette may not be the best dancer, but that didn't stop her from becoming the star of the show.

“I dance, for I miss you day and night.”
Goods.20131105_Desc:
Yvette's outfit for the Wilderness Winter Challenge. The elastic warm fleece is suitable for all winter outdoor activities, making it her favorite winter clothing.

“Are you cold? I don't feel cold at all.”
Goods.20131106_Desc:
The outfit Yvette wears to the Safety Day event. A sharp contrast to her usual cool-toned clothing, this outfit replicates a look from a fairy tale. However, unlike the protagonist in the story, she would not surrender without a fight.

【“Would you accept... my safety apple?”】
Goods.20131103_Desc:
Yvette's outfit for her internship at the café. On the navigator's advice, she took the job to improve her communication skills. Although Yvette tried to serve the customers, she was baffled to discover that they were more interested in serving her.

“Fay wouldn't know what to make of this either, sir...”
Goods.20131004_Desc: Yvette's spare lab coat. The soft orange makes her look even sweeter and more charming.
Goods.20131007_Desc: Yvette's spare lab coat. The touching warmth is buried deep in the snow.
Goods.20131006_Desc: Yvette's spare lab coat. The bright yellow brings a warm feeling to the heart.
Goods.20131008_Desc: Yvette's spare lab coat. The lush summer leaves can hardly conceal the girl's thoughts.
Goods.20131005_Desc: Yvette's spare lab coat. The budding green resembles fresh sprouts under the sunlight.
Goods.20131003_Desc: Yvette's spare lab coat. Beneath her cold exterior, there lies a fiery heart.
Goods.20131002_Desc: Yvette's spare lab coat. The vibrant purple makes her as graceful as a slender lavender.
Goods.20131102_Desc:
Yvette's beach outfit radiates youthful energy and a refreshing vibe, grabbing everyone's attention, much like a cute panda.

"Pandas are bears too," Yvette giggles, touching her ears. "At least Fei won’t feel alone at the summer music fest with a fellow bear around."
Goods.20131101_Desc:
Yvette's outfit for outdoor excursions. The simple, unembellished style reflects her pure heart. Of course, she occasionally shows her cute, girlish side.

【“Eh? You would like to have lunch with us? But I can't find Fay...”
“How about you and I have lunch in secret this time...”
Can Yvette really not find Fay? Or...
She is the only one who can give you the answer to that question.】
Goods.22108112_Desc: You won't get away with it!
Goods.31001048_Desc:
“It is rumored that there is a bar called The Sanctuary at 53 Hummingbird Avenue. The establishment serves all kinds of fine wines while soothing music is played and lights flicker. Some visitors compare it with paradise, while others say it is not open to the public.”
【“Can you find the way to enter the night?”】
Goods.31000130_Desc: It is said that those who watch fireworks holding hands will be together forever.
Goods.20205052_Desc: It's rumored that Galatea designed this dress after gazing at the night sky for half an hour. Others say the inspiration struck after her visit to the Cloudscape Gallery's jewelry exhibition. Galatea neither confirms nor denies these rumors. "Stars and gemstones are quite similar, aren't they?"
Goods.20110102_Desc:
Rumor has it that there is a highly skilled young man who shows up in the auto shop from time to time. No matter what the malfunction is or the age of a race car, as long as he repairs and tunes it, the vehicle's performance will be enhanced. Everyone praises his repair skills, but few inquire about his identity - this is exactly what he aims to achieve.

“Check out the repair. There's nothing my wrench can't fix.”
“However, the parts are severely worn. You gotta take care of your car, buddy.”
“Feel like you've seen me before? Well, it's a large city. Perhaps you have; perhaps you haven't. Don't overthink it.”
Goods.20133055_Desc: An elegant outfit symbolizing scales of justice. A noble adjudicator shall deliver judgments for the world.
Goods.20137102_Desc:
An outfit designed for the promotional event of Kanami's new song.

HelpTipsUI.9_Content:
<CommonRulePopUp_18_Blod>Earning Union Merit and EXP</>
1. Play matches with your Union to earn Union Merit. The amount depends on the mode and match outcome.
2. Participate in event matches to earn Union Merit. The amount depends on the match outcome.
3. If negative behavior is detected in a match, Union Merit will not be awarded.
4. Any Union Merit earned will convert to Union EXP at a 1:1 ratio.

<CommonRulePopUp_18_Blod>Weekly Union EXP Limit</>
Union EXP earned each week is capped. Once the limit is reached, no more Union EXP can be earned.
Resets every Monday at 6:00 AM.

<CommonRulePopUp_18_Blod>Level Rewards</>
1. Earn the required amount of Union Merit in your current Union to claim level rewards.
2. Memory Sequences, Dimension Gift Boxes, and EXP Bonus Cards are one-time rewards. Once claimed, they cannot be reclaimed by switching Unions.
3. Medals, player cards, and cases are Union privilege rewards and cannot be used if you leave the Union.

<CommonRulePopUp_18_Blod>Union Inactivity Penalty</>
If all Union members have been offline for more than 7 days, Union EXP will be deducted daily at 6:00 AM until a member logs in.
HelpTipsUI.12_Content:
<CommonRulePopUp_18_Blod>Cumulative Top-Up Notice</>

1. Top up a certain amount to claim corresponding tier rewards.
2. Purchases of Monthly Pass, Season Pass, Exclusive Packs, etc., are calculated based on the amount of Bablo Crystals converted.
HelpTipsUI.8_Content:
<CommonRulePopUp_18_Blod>Leader Rights</>
The leader can approve members, remove members, transfer leadership, and edit Union details.

<CommonRulePopUp_18_Blod>Deputy Leader Rights</>
The leader can appoint up to 2 deputy leaders. Deputies can approve and remove members.

<CommonRulePopUp_18_Blod>Automatic Leader Transfer</>
If the leader is inactive for more than 14 days, leadership will automatically transfer to an active Union member.
HelpTipsUI.10_Content:
<CommonRulePopUp_18_Blod>Extra account EXP and Dream Tokens</>
Playing matches with your Union grants additional account EXP and Dream Tokens.
The bonus varies depending on the number of Union members.

<CommonRulePopUp_18_Blod>There is a limit to the weekly bonus</>
Bonuses reset every Monday at 6:00 AM
HelpTipsUI.11_Content: Servers determine your current network node. To ensure a stable connection and optimal gameplay, you can't switch servers frequently.

HuiXing_146_Lv_0.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId146: So, what’s your plan for the rest of the day?
HuiXing_146_Lv_0.Row4_PlayerOption2: I didn't realize Astral Sanctuary had branches.
HuiXing_146_Lv_0.Row9_PlayerOption2: I'll wander around for a bit.
HuiXing_146_Lv_0.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Sure, feel free to drop by anytime. The door unlocks with a facial scan.
HuiXing_146_Lv_0.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId146: In that case, enjoy your stroll, Navigator.
HuiXing_146_Lv_0.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Haha, that was my exact reaction when I first got the map too.
HuiXing_146_Lv_0.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId146: I’ve sent the map to you as well.
HuiXing_146_Lv_0.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId146: If I'm not around, I'm probably attending to a patient, so you might need to wait a bit.
HuiXing_146_Lv_0.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId146: I tend to spend more time at this branch, helping the people in this community.
HuiXing_146_Lv_0.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Star Street, East 198th District, Strian. This is where the Astral Sanctuary branch is located.
HuiXing_146_Lv_0.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId146: You'd be surprised; it’s not as bustling as Area 88, but the quiet here has its own charm that I really enjoy.
HuiXing_146_Lv_0.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId146: If there's anything you need, don't hesitate to ask.
HuiXing_146_Lv_0.Row9_PlayerOption1: I'll pop by to check out your branch.
HuiXing_146_Lv_0.Row4_PlayerOption1: Now I won't take the wrong train again.

HuiXing_146_Lv_1.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId146: By "latest," I mean I create a unique blend every day.
HuiXing_146_Lv_1.Row3_PlayerOption1: Actually, I don't really drink coffee.
HuiXing_146_Lv_1.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId146: By tweaking these meticulously, I can enrich the flavor, even making it taste like cola if you wish!
HuiXing_146_Lv_1.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Since you've come all the way here, would you like to try my latest brew of Starlight Coffee?
HuiXing_146_Lv_1.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId146: I'll do my best to show you the charm of Starlight Coffee.
HuiXing_146_Lv_1.Row2_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Do you have any particular preferences?
HuiXing_146_Lv_1.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Since I'm managing Astral Sanctuary all on my own, coffee is the only option I can offer...
HuiXing_146_Lv_1.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId146: There's a lot that goes into a cup of coffee. You need to think about the water volume, grind size, extraction rate, and more...
HuiXing_146_Lv_1.Row8_PlayerOption1: Wow, now you've got my attention!

HuiXing_146_Lv_10.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId146: I'm sure it’ll all work out.
HuiXing_146_Lv_10.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId146: After tons of prep work, it's finally happening!
HuiXing_146_Lv_10.Row8_PlayerOption1: Haha, fingers crossed the weather’s perfect that night.
HuiXing_146_Lv_10.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Yep! We’re planning a public stargazing event at Astral Sanctuary.
HuiXing_146_Lv_10.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId146: So, I hope you can take a well-deserved break.
HuiXing_146_Lv_10.RowNewRow_0_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Delete the records according to the actual situation.
HuiXing_146_Lv_10.Row2_PlayerOption1: You seem to be in a good mood.
HuiXing_146_Lv_10.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId146: It's been pretty cloudy lately, but as long as there's wind tonight, we should have clear skies.
HuiXing_146_Lv_10.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId146: And I know I’ve asked you for a lot of help before...

HuiXing_146_Lv_2.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId146: The V23.8.19.62 significantly improves upon the overly mild taste of V14.3.2.44.
HuiXing_146_Lv_2.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId146: But for some reason, everyone keeps politely turning down my offer to try it...
HuiXing_146_Lv_2.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId146: I've perfected the latest version of Starlight Coffee V23.8.19.62.
HuiXing_146_Lv_2.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Um, there's something I need to tell you...
HuiXing_146_Lv_2.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Oh... it's the first time someone agreed so readily! I knew I could count on you!
HuiXing_146_Lv_2.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Great, let's meet in the canteen after work!
HuiXing_146_Lv_2.Row14_PlayerOption1: It's no big deal, I'd love to try it.
HuiXing_146_Lv_2.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId146: I've added a bunch of real ingredients, like fragrant mint, white orchid, jasmine tea, oat flakes, even tuna.
HuiXing_146_Lv_2.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId146: So, I was really hoping you could...
HuiXing_146_Lv_2.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId146: It took me a lot of effort, and it'd be such a shame if no one could appreciate it...
HuiXing_146_Lv_2.Row8_PlayerOption2: What's up with that ridiculously long version number?

HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Don't tell me you're in on it too?
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId146: You're not supposed to hear yourself talking in your sleep, right?
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row5_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Three all-nighters in a row... Definitely not doing that again...
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId146: I'm asking because I just had a super weird moment.
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row17_TextContent_FromRoleId146: And you are definitely helping me out with it!
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Do I often talk in my sleep?
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row8_TextContent_FromRoleId146: But during my nap, I actually did hear myself...
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Eh? Kokona was here? She probably saw me napping and decided not to wake me.
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row13_PlayerOption2: You know what they say about snitches...
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Haha, I knew it! She definitely recorded me sleep-talking.
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row4_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Eh? Don't tell me it's V23.8.19.62? Ugh...
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row12_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Hmm... Did she have a mischievous grin on her face when she was leaving?
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row16_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Mmm... Looks like I'll have to give Kokona a special "welcome" the next time she visits.
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.RowNewRow_0_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Delete the records according to the actual situation.
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row2_PlayerOption2: Yeah, you keep repeating Starlight Coffee version numbers.
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row2_PlayerOption1: Yeah, you keep repeating dessert names.
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row13_PlayerOption1: Yep, she was smirking and fiddling with a recorder.
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId146: Thinking about it now... It's so strange...
HuiXing_146_Lv_6.Row10_PlayerOption1: By the way, Kokona dropped by at Astral Sanctuary earlier.

IdCard.31002002_Desc:
“Have you ever truly looked at the starry sky?”
“I heard there is a unique star for everyone, waiting alone in the universe, hoping someone would gaze at it.”
“If one day you see an unusual light in the sky, that's probably your star winking at you.”
“Where is my star? Well... that's a secret.”

The girl never stops chasing the night sky.
Through countless nights under the stars, she patiently waits for that one star in the vast galaxy to reveal itself.
One day, the star winks at her.
And the entire night sky changes its colors.
IdCard.31002005_Desc:
【“Whether it's going on an adventure or simply sleeping in, one must do what they love the most on a rare off day!”
Having finished a day's work, Kokona changes into comfortable clothes and lays down.

Next to her are stacks of boxes and all kinds of items.
Among them are memorabilia she has not had time to organize and essential tools for her future explorations.
“Come on. Don't just stand there. Help me out.”】
IdCard.31002007_Desc:
“It's not that I don't like going out...”
The girl shyly pulls down the brim of her bear hoodie. “It's just that there are too many people outside, and it's noisy... At home, I have Fay, blankets, and endless chilled drinks...”
“I think it's really nice to just stay at home... W-Wouldn't you agree?”
IdCard.31002006_Desc:
“Today, I have to design a children's book for Astral Sanctuary. As for tomorrow, I promised my neighbor I'd help her design her living room...”
It is another incredibly fulfilling day for the girl who finds joy in helping others. But this time, you notice a hint of weariness in her expression.

“Hold on, Navigator. Stay still!
There! That's perfect!”
The girl exclaims, as if she’s discovered the rarest treasure.
“It's your day off... will you model for me?”
She approaches you, her most trusted person, with a warmth only for you, her eyes solely focused on you.
IdCard.31002009_Desc:
【“Would you like another taiyaki? Or a sweet shark?”
Sitting on a floor mat, Fuchsia extends her hands to me, offering a piece of taiyaki in one and a sweet shark in the other - a dilemma of sweetness.
Although it is really tempting, I have already had too many sweet snacks today. I swallow as I firmly refuse Fuchsia's offer.
“Suit yourself.” Fuchsia shrugs before taking a huge bite, licking the crumbs from the corner of her mouth. Then, she stretches lazily and sprawls on the floor.
“This is how you should spend your holiday.”】
IdCard.31002004_Desc:
【“What flower is this? It's an orchid.”
The floral fragrance of the tea wafts from the cups in front of Lawine and you.
The pale petals unfold in your cup of tea.
You notice that a similar flower is embroidered on her clothes.

“Orchids only bloom in spring, a season far too short in this world.”
As she sips some tea, the girl in front of you smiles, barely perceptible.
For her, this brief respite from all her responsibilities and duties is her spring.】
IdCard.31002003_Desc:
【After playing a violin piece, Audrey sits next to you.
“Why do you still look so gloomy when I'm with you?”
“What are you worried about? The test we have to face? Or the inevitable collapse?”

She pours two cups of black tea and places one before of you.
“Let go of all the troubles. Let us toast to hardship and... this world.”
As the cups touch, producing a crisp sound,  the girl smiles confidently.】
IdCard.31002008_Desc:
【As an idol, Kanami enjoys spending time on makeup and styles.
Whether it's a natural look or an elegant stage look, Kanami excels at putting them on, skillfully applying any makeup products.
As Kanami finishes her makeup, she draws a cute mark on the mirror with her lipstick.
“Navigator, will you be colored by my hues?”】
IdCard.31002001_Desc:
【As a super gamer, Michele owns many stylish and casual outfits. However, as she is also a cat lady, she prefers this cute cat-themed outfit, whether for its comfort or adorable cat-like colors.

“A cat showing its belly is a sign of being friendly and feeling safe.” The girl says, smiling.

Michele has changed her flashy gamer gear into a cute girl's outfit. Is the cat-like girl trying to tell you something?】
IdCard.31001002_Desc:
Having become a frontline investigator, Michele carries with her the will of all her predecessors. When a badge number is reactivated, the pitiful criminals better tremble in fear, for the successor of the White Tiger will defeat every single one of them.

“Listen up! I have you surrounded! Surrender now!” Michele once intimidated suspects like this during operations.
And she kept her word, singlehandedly arresting over a dozen suspects.
"I thought I wouldn't see the light of day again. Was she going to devour us like a wild tiger?" a criminal recalls, trembling in fear.
IdCard.31000178_Desc: 【The shark in the tank does not realize its freedom is lost, nor does it feel any pain. People pity it for losing the dignity of a predator, but the shark does not care.】
IdCard.31001001_Desc:
The royal swordswoman, enchanting as a rose, gazes into the distance.
She sees nothing but carnage and rivers of blood.
The rose-decorated sword pierces an enemy's heart.
The rose is dyed in blood's hue; shadows cast wide their pall.
Her mind, like the breeze, wanders far, unconfined by any wall.
“For you alone, the flowers unveil their bloom; should they fade, what sorrow calls?”

Care for a game of chess with me?

Designed by Urbino’s Cloudscape Gallery for combat teams, this Case blends a mechanical style with string elements, symbolizing relentless progress.

Medal Slots: 2

A standard case designed by Urbino’s Cloudscape Gallery. Its simple and elegant design radiates a back-to-basics beauty.

Medal Slots: 2

An artistic case designed by Urbino’s Cloudscape Gallery. It features a bright red color scheme, suitable for starting a year of good fortune.

Medal Slots: 2

[Season 3 Advanced Warrant Exclusive]

Medal Slots: 3
IdCard.32000008_Desc:
An artistic case designed by Urbino’s Cloudscape Gallery. It features a dark and white-gray palette, symbolizing the dark clouds of an impending storm.

[Season 2 Advanced Warrant PLUS Exclusive]

Medal Slots: 3
IdCard.32000011_Desc:
An artistic case designed by Urbino’s Cloudscape Gallery. Inspired by the golden flames of victory, it's a cherished keepsake from the Navigator's participation in the open beta.

Medal Slots: 2
IdCard.32000024_Desc:
A fragrant case designed by Cloudburst Museum, a subsidiary of Urbino. Inspired by the Fragrans Immersion series, its unique aroma wraps around the body like an invisible ribbon.

[Season 1 Advanced Warrant PLUS Exclusive]

Medal Slots: 3
IdCard.32000006_Desc:
The Type VI case is designed by Rainbow Workshop, a subsidiary of Urbino. The frame of the chip is outlined with a blue line representing P.U.S and a red line representing The Scissors. Its overall design reflects Urbino's neutral and inclusive stance.

[Season 1 Advanced Warrant Exclusive]

Medal Slots: 3
IdCard.32000005_Desc:
The Type V case is designed by Gray Matter Medical, a subsidiary of Urbino. Different from past cases, the Type V features an artistic side-cutting scheme. This was the first time in the history of Strinova that a manufacturer attempted the artistic cutting of memory chips, significantly advancing the commercialization of memory chips.

Medal Slots: 2
IdCard.32000003_Desc:
The Type III case is designed by Black Box Technology, a subsidiary of Urbino. It boldly adopts a brand-new asymmetric cutting scheme. While it never became a mainstream chip case, it has gained a lot of popularity among a small number of loyal users.

Medal Slots: 2
IdCard.32000004_Desc:
The Type IV case is designed by Black Box Technology, a subsidiary of Urbino. It features a corner-trimming cutting scheme and an innovative hidden routing pattern. While its revolution routing pattern was not mass-produced, it played a decisive role in the development of subsequent case.

Medal Slots: 2
IdCard.32000015_Desc:
Standard packaging produced by the Wilderness Adventure Foundation in P.U.S. As a souvenir for adventurers. It is said that the design is inspired by the legend of the ancient Golden Kingdom.

Medal Slots: 3
IdCard.32000013_Desc:
A non-standard Case crafted by Preton's charity artist, with orange flames heralding the arrival of a hero…

[Season 4 Advanced Search Warrant Exclusive]

Medal Slots: 3
IdCard.32000014_Desc:
Produced by the Grove family, this artistic Case from the "Aesthetics and Style" event is inspired by maid attire. On the pure white body, a butterfly dances gracefully.

Medal Slots: 2
IdCard.32000002_Desc:
The Type II casing is designed by Wisdom, an official department of P.U.S. Featuring a three-sided cutting scheme and symmetrical routing pattern, it is highly integrable and often used in scientific research.

Medal Slots: 2
IdCard.31000174_Desc: Currents, waves, and sound are in synergy, stirring up a new storm.
IdCard.32000016_Desc:
A standard Case by Cloudscape Gallery, featuring a layered design inspired by the industrial old town of Preton...

Season 5 Advanced Warrant Exclusive

Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row14_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Going to food stalls after work is the best way to meet new friends.
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row16_PlayerOption2: I'd like to have some refreshing after work.
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row11_TextContent_FromRoleId124: But if you want to make friends quickly, the best way is to go out to restaurants together!
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row12_PlayerOption1: You don't seem to be talking about an ordinary restaurant
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row10_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Haha... we might have just discovered the secret to world peace!
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row3_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Hello! Navigator, my name is Kokona.
Kokona_124_Lv_1.RowStart_TextContent_FromRoleId124: Looks like the friend request went through.
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row16_PlayerOption1: If it's a food stall... it's gotta be barbecue
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row22_TextContent_FromRoleId124: By the way, there's going to be a taste-testing soon. Let's go together!
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row9_TextContent_FromRoleId124: That's right... why didn't I think of that?
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row15_TextContent_FromRoleId124: What would you like to eat, Navigator? I'll treat you next time!
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row12_PlayerOption2: A very down-to-earth way to put it.
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row20-b_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I know, I know. We can't go without some ice-cold soda!
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row6_TextContent_FromRoleId124: I've already heard quite a lot about you.
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row7_TextContent_FromRoleId124: The friend of my friend is also my friend. That's why I also want to get to know you, Navigator!
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row13_TextContent_FromRoleId124: That's right. We need something grander than a regular restaurant.
Kokona_124_Lv_1.Row8_PlayerOption1: If you keep this up, won't you befriend the whole world?
