RoleSkin.20101101_Description:
A sporty baseball uniform with playful cat ears and a tail. Donning this outfit, Michele seems impressively agile and sharp.

“Steal! Steal! Steal! Base after base!”
As the audience's thunderous cheering fills the stadium, Michele dashes to second base.
Not only is she a super good gamer, Michele is also great at sports.
Her glistening sweat and bright, sunny smile are the most beautiful sight on the field.
RoleSkin.20133107_Description:
A mysterious guest has appeared at the underground bar. No one knows what brought her here or what secrets she holds.

"Are you sure we haven't met before? I can't help but feel like I've asked you this exact question many times before."
RoleSkin.20109057_Description: In sharp contrast to Reiichi's indifferent demeanor, this outfit features patterns of raging flames. Even the coldest of tools need to be driven by heat.
RoleSkin.20101105_Description:
In stark contrast to her usual authoritative demeanor, Michele becomes a mischievous demon straight out of a fairy tale.
 
[Knock, knock. “Open up. It's Investigator Michele from the underworld. I'm here to inspect your snack stash today!”
Donning this outfit, Michele appears happier than usual.
But she's still herself. So, it should be fine, right?]
RoleSkin.20108101_Description:
Nobunaga's exclusive P.U.S. Spec Ops suit blends steel and leather, yet his elegance and calm demeanor remain undiminished.

“Activate remote control and the radar system. Don’t let anything slip past.”
Under Nobunaga's command, a meticulous raid is underway.
However, the operation ended before it even began.
"You must be the target. So, will you surrender? Or will you make me do it?"
RoleSkin.20901001_Description: The question mark displayed on players who join mid-match
RoleSkin.20901002_Description: The question mark displayed on players who join mid-match
RoleSkin.20101051_Description:
Michele leapt at the chance to customize her own racing outfit for the Port Euler Jet Ski Grand Prix.

Three, two, one... Go!!!
RoleSkin.20131058_Description: In order to study the impact of letters on people's emotions, Yvette dons the courier's outfit, delivering letters to different households to feel their sentiments. However, when looking at the person she wants to send a letter to, Yvette notices her heartbeat suddenly accelerating.
RoleSkin.20124001_Description: Kokona's custom sniper suit is fully functional with a modest design, suitable for all weather conditions.
RoleSkin.20133053_Description: A special outfit customized for Meredith with a diamond core symbolizing her sharp, rational, and unwavering resolve.
RoleSkin.20133101_Description:
While working for P.U.S, Meredith once led a team to explore the True Wilderness. She designed this outfit to embody the spirit of adventure.

“If explorers halt due to the fear of the unknown, it will undermine humanity's courage and future.”
RoleSkin.20109103_Description:
A special combat suit designed for experimental high-energy electromagnetic weapons, with enhanced insulation based on Reiichi's combat experience.
The silent sniper enters the battlefield, channeling intense energy.

“Careful. You might get a shock.”
RoleSkin.20107101_Description:
It's been said that an explorer who can't fish isn't a true artist.
To visit the remote ecological zones in Strian's countryside for field sketches, Maddelena prepared this outdoor set. She journeys along the river, alternating between sketching and fishing, filling her canvas and fish basket.

"Yes! Got one! Don't run away! Taste my paint bubbles!”
RoleSkin.20112051_Description:
Since when
have we been trapped within the confines of towering steel?
The starry sky grows dim,
no longer illuminating the path arrived on.
RoleSkin.20109105_Description:
Reiichi's outfit for chess exhibition matches. The fedora and the extra wide lapel add a touch of leisure to the elegance, while the plain glasses provide a unique impression. Together with the dyed hair, one would not recognize him if not a close acquaintance.

“How many times have I told you? The whole point of the Queen's Gambit is to ensure the safety of the central board. Now isn't the time to sweat over a single pawn.”
RoleSkin.20109101_Description:
Reiichi's outfit for eavesdropping missions.
Blending in is part of being a spy, even in a café.

"Today, there will be... a different kind of rain."
RoleSkin.20109102_Description:
Reiichi prepared this diving suit while on a seaside vacation. While most of the gadgets on it are functional, it also features some fancy trinkets.

【“Phew... There are many beautiful corals even in the sea.”
As Reiichi emerges from the sea after diving, he shows a faint smile.
The usually indifferent man seems to genuinely enjoy this seaside trip.
“Relax. I'm an easy guy to get along with.”
You feel like you have seen a rare side of Reiichi.】
RoleSkin.20109003_Description: A variant of Reiichi's combat uniform. Even in total darkness, he harbors a glimmer of hope.
RoleSkin.20109007_Description: A variant of Reiichi's combat uniform. The army green symbolizes his discipline.
RoleSkin.20109005_Description:
Reiichi's backup combat suit. Fully functional, its combat capabilities are comparable to the original.

“Do not stop fighting. Do not despair.”
RoleSkin.20109004_Description: Reiichi's backup combat suit. The deep blue hue sings a song of sorrow.
RoleSkin.20109008_Description: A variant of Reiichi's combat uniform. The light blue shirt symbolizes the clear sky in his heart.
RoleSkin.20109002_Description: Reiichi's backup combat suit, with a mysterious purple lining, conceals his many burdens.
RoleSkin.20109009_Description: A variant of Reiichi's combat uniform. The dim green symbolizes his nearly withered yet undying hope.
RoleSkin.20109010_Description: A variant of Reiichi's combat uniform. The bright shirt contrasts sharply with the dark coat. He rarely wears it.
RoleSkin.20109001_Description: Reiichi's favorite outfit. It is comfortable, simple, practical, and reliable, exuding the firm will of a warrior.
RoleSkin.20109104_Description:
Reiichi's personal outfit, customized based on old space suits. Though partly resembling the original, it has been modified for combat readiness in case of emergency missions. Had there been conflict in the world, perhaps Reiichi would have become an astronaut, scattering his brilliant ideas across the vast universe.

【“Air pressure normal; temperature normal... It's a pity a propulsion device couldn't be fitted.”】
RoleSkin.20109106_Description:
Reiichi’s special gear for infiltrating the black market emphasizes the mystical allure of Eastern charm and his personal style. The pendant he wears is made from polished scrap, not a genuine antique, but convincing enough to pass as one.

“Heh... You've got a good eye. This is top-notch stuff.”
RoleSkin.20128101_Description:
Inspired by bamboo, this elegant outfit evokes a sense of peace, filled with Lawine's longing for her homeland.

【In her spare time, she often visits her cabin in the bamboo forest.
Through the gaps in the bamboo forest, the sun shines on the dim wooden floor.
Even with you by her side, she remains silent nonetheless.
Quietly, she hands you a fresh cup of tea.】
RoleSkin.20131054_Description: A cute lab coat decorated with clovers. Hope, faith, love, and fortune —Yvette wishes all these good things to be with you.
RoleSkin.20107104_Description:
A space-themed white bodysuit featuring stylish mecha rabbit ears, making Maddelena seem less simple and more daring than usual.
 
 “Look! Doesn't the reflection of this outfit resemble moonlight?”
 “I heard that a bunny lived happily on the Moon. Could there be a mecha bunny on Strinova's moon as well?”
 The girl happily dreams of space under the cover of the night.
RoleSkin.20105053_Description: An elegant outfit inspired by playing cards. Hearts, Diamonds, Spades, and Clubs... Where's the Ace? Of course, it's Audrey herself!
RoleSkin.20132206_Description: Named after the ancient "Lei Loong," this heroic attire features motifs of dragons and crackling lightning. It accompanies its master across lands and seas, becoming a legendary tale among adventurers.
RoleSkin.20132207_Description: Named after the ancient "Lei Loong," this heroic attire features motifs of dragons and crackling lightning. It accompanies its master across lands and seas, becoming a legendary tale among adventurers.
RoleSkin.20132208_Description: Named after the ancient "Lei Loong," this heroic attire features motifs of dragons and crackling lightning. It accompanies its master across lands and seas, becoming a legendary tale among adventurers.
RoleSkin.20132209_Description: Named after the ancient "Lei Loong," this heroic attire features motifs of dragons and crackling lightning. It accompanies its master across lands and seas, becoming a legendary tale among adventurers.
RoleSkin.20132210_Description: Named after the ancient "Lei Loong," this heroic attire features motifs of dragons and crackling lightning. It accompanies its master across lands and seas, becoming a legendary tale among adventurers.
RoleSkin.20105206_Description: A Grove ceremonial gown inspired by the pale lily. Featuring a single-shoulder cape representing the dignity and glory of the Grove family, the outfit serves as a reminder of Audrey's inexperience and determination when first taking on family responsibilities.
RoleSkin.20105207_Description: A Grove ceremonial gown inspired by the pale lily. Featuring a single-shoulder cape representing the dignity and glory of the Grove family, the outfit serves as a reminder of Audrey's inexperience and determination when first taking on family responsibilities.
RoleSkin.20105208_Description: A Grove ceremonial gown inspired by the pale lily. Featuring a single-shoulder cape representing the dignity and glory of the Grove family, the outfit serves as a reminder of Audrey's inexperience and determination when first taking on family responsibilities.
RoleSkin.20105209_Description: A Grove ceremonial gown inspired by the pale lily. Featuring a single-shoulder cape representing the dignity and glory of the Grove family, the outfit serves as a reminder of Audrey's inexperience and determination when first taking on family responsibilities.
RoleSkin.20105210_Description: A Grove ceremonial gown inspired by the pale lily. Featuring a single-shoulder cape representing the dignity and glory of the Grove family, the outfit serves as a reminder of Audrey's inexperience and determination when first taking on family responsibilities.
RoleSkin.20108103_Description:
An outfit inspired by cranes, featuring two white cranes painted on a black background as if they are soaring from an inky pine forest, chasing daylight.
Nobunaga always feels nostalgic when he dons this outfit. During the P.U.S Investigator course, he learned ancient Eastern military strategies—"Crane Wing Formation" was once their forte, requiring two partners to flank the enemy from both sides. Even without a partner, Nobunaga has managed to adapt the same tactics for solo combat.

“I have you surrounded. Surrender now.”
RoleSkin.20131206_Description: Yvette's dress for the P.U.S ball. While she still feels shy about dressing so formally, she finds it nice to show a different side of herself every now and then.
RoleSkin.20131207_Description: Yvette's dress for the P.U.S ball. While she still feels shy about dressing so formally, she finds it nice to show a different side of herself every now and then.
RoleSkin.20131208_Description: Yvette's dress for the P.U.S ball. While she still feels shy about dressing so formally, she finds it nice to show a different side of herself every now and then.
RoleSkin.20131209_Description: Yvette's dress for the P.U.S ball. While she still feels shy about dressing so formally, she finds it nice to show a different side of herself every now and then.
RoleSkin.20131210_Description: Yvette's dress for the P.U.S ball. While she still feels shy about dressing so formally, she finds it nice to show a different side of herself every now and then.
RoleSkin.20131107_Description:
Yvette's outfit for the Urbino talent show. The light dress evokes poetic scenery of ancient civilizations. Yvette may not be the best dancer, but that didn't stop her from becoming the star of the show.

“I dance, for I miss you day and night.”
RoleSkin.20131105_Description:
Yvette's outfit for the Wilderness Winter Challenge. The elastic warm fleece is suitable for all winter outdoor activities, making it her favorite winter clothing.

“Are you cold? I don't feel cold at all.”
RoleSkin.20131106_Description:
The outfit Yvette wears to the Safety Day event. A sharp contrast to her usual cool-toned clothing, this outfit replicates a look from a fairy tale. However, unlike the protagonist in the story, she would not surrender without a fight.

【“Would you accept... my safety apple?”】
RoleSkin.20131103_Description:
Yvette's outfit for her internship at the café. On the navigator's advice, she took the job to improve her communication skills. Although Yvette tried to serve the customers, she was baffled to discover that they were more interested in serving her.

“Fay wouldn't know what to make of this either, sir...”
RoleSkin.20131004_Description: Yvette's spare lab coat. The soft orange makes her look even sweeter and more charming.
RoleSkin.20131007_Description: Yvette's spare lab coat. The touching warmth is buried deep in the snow.
RoleSkin.20131006_Description: Yvette's spare lab coat. The bright yellow brings a warm feeling to the heart.
RoleSkin.20131008_Description: Yvette's spare lab coat. The lush summer leaves can hardly conceal the girl's thoughts.
RoleSkin.20131005_Description: Yvette's spare lab coat. The budding green resembles fresh sprouts under the sunlight.
RoleSkin.20131003_Description: Yvette's spare lab coat. Beneath her cold exterior, there lies a fiery heart.
RoleSkin.20131002_Description: Yvette's spare lab coat. The vibrant purple makes her as graceful as a slender lavender.
RoleSkin.20131102_Description:
"Yvette's beach outfit radiates youthful energy and a refreshing vibe, grabbing everyone's attention, much like a cute panda.

"Pandas are bears too," Yvette giggles, touching her ears. "At least Fei won’t feel alone at the summer music fest with a fellow bear around.""
RoleSkin.20131001_Description: Yvette's favorite lab coat. The pair of teddy ears on the hood reveals her childlike innocence.
RoleSkin.20131101_Description:
Yvette's outfit for outdoor excursions. The simple, unembellished style reflects her pure heart. Of course, she occasionally shows her cute, girlish side.

【“Eh? You would like to have lunch with us? But I can't find Fay...”
“How about you and I have lunch in secret this time...”
Can Yvette really not find Fay? Or...
She is the only one who can give you the answer to that question.】
RoleSkin.20205052_Description: It's rumored that Galatea designed this dress after gazing at the night sky for half an hour. Others say the inspiration struck after her visit to the Cloudscape Gallery's jewelry exhibition. Galatea neither confirms nor denies these rumors. "Stars and gemstones are quite similar, aren't they?"
RoleSkin.20110102_Description:
Rumor has it that there is a highly skilled young man who shows up in the auto shop from time to time. No matter what the malfunction is or the age of a race car, as long as he repairs and tunes it, the vehicle's performance will be enhanced. Everyone praises his repair skills, but few inquire about his identity - this is exactly what he aims to achieve.

“Check out the repair. There's nothing my wrench can't fix.”
“However, the parts are severely worn. You gotta take care of your car, buddy.”
“Feel like you've seen me before? Well, it's a large city. Perhaps you have; perhaps you haven't. Don't overthink it.”
RoleSkin.20133055_Description: An elegant outfit symbolizing scales of justice. A noble adjudicator shall deliver judgments for the world.
RoleSkin.20137102_Description:
An outfit designed for the promotional event of Kanami's new song.
After several modifications, it strikes a perfect balance between the distance of an idol and the closeness of a maid. However, she seems to have another reason for liking this outfit...

"Kanami is everyone's idol, but... for now, let me provide you with an exclusive maid café experience."
RoleSkin.20108107_Description:
Nobunaga's outfit for chess exhibition matches. The black and white checkered pattern and smooth lines exude a sense of fashion and elegance, making it Nobunaga's perfect “armor” for important occasions. Nobunaga used to be weary of the Bureau of Investigation's participation in such events, but...

“I thought you and I were just like these two pieces, never truly able to touch one another.”
RoleSkin.20108104_Description:
Nobunaga's racing suit for the Winter Wilderness Challenges offers great thermal insulation. The snow goggles and snug fit aid in securing the lead during snow races.

“Nobunaga! Again! That's his third Winter Wilderness title!”
RoleSkin.20108008_Description: Nobunaga's spare work outfit. The light fades, leaving only ashes.
RoleSkin.20108004_Description: Nobunaga's spare work outfit, surging with emotions like waves rolling in.
RoleSkin.20108007_Description: Nobunaga's spare work outfit—the rust does not hide his lofty ambition.
RoleSkin.20108003_Description: Nobunaga's spare work outfit, symbolizing his will to break through obstacles like flying sparks.
RoleSkin.20108005_Description: Nobunaga's spare work outfit. The flashing lightning represents his courage and wisdom.
RoleSkin.20108006_Description: Nobunaga's spare work outfit. The dazzling amethyst represents his elegance and pride.
RoleSkin.20108002_Description: Nobunaga's spare work outfit, as fearless as a clear sky after rain.
RoleSkin.20108056_Description: Nobunaga's custom uniform features the rich green of a bamboo forest, perfectly highlighting the wearer's calm demeanor.
RoleSkin.20108105_Description:
Nobunaga's street performance outfit shows his take on rock 'n' roll. Some say rock is about guitar solos, bass lines, and drum beats. Others see it as a spirit, a rebellion against hypocrisy, the city's voice, and a musical outcry. For Nobunaga, rock is a revolution, blending speed, power, and the bright burst of life.

"Chaos isn't just about overturning old rules; it’s the origin of a new order."
RoleSkin.20108108_Description:
Nobunaga dons this outfit when he is in charge of security at theater events. Inspired by the Mediterranean culture of old Earth, the design features a deep, understated style, conveying a sense of freedom and mystery.

“Toiling in the darkness, serving the light - Was it the same for that person?”
RoleSkin.20115103_Description:
Wearing a beautiful dress, Flavia is as glamorous as a dazzling peacock, capturing the spotlight on the dance floor.

"Don't stress about it. Leave it to me. As your dance partner, I'll take care of you."
RoleSkin.20124054_Description: A work outfit similar to that of a taxi driver, yet exceptionally striking because of the wearer. Kokona says it is her disguise, but is that really the case?
RoleSkin.20146055_Description: The elegant purple dress accentuates Celestia's mysterious elegance. It suits her well, but she never speaks of the story behind it.
RoleSkin.20105054_Description: The elegant blue dress with luxurious gold patterns is Audrey's go-to gown for formal occasions. As the face of Grove Enterprise, she sees social events as just another battlefield.
RoleSkin.20133054_Description: The stunning violet blooms in the barren wilderness, not for others, but to shine alone. The beauty of a solitary orchid in a secluded valley needs no admiration.
RoleSkin.20205007_Description: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. Its color scheme is rumored to have been inspired by top-grade chrysoberyl gemstones.
RoleSkin.20205002_Description: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. Its color scheme is rumored to have been inspired by the colors of a peacock's eye.
RoleSkin.20205005_Description: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. Its color scheme is rumored to have been inspired by a gloomy night with impending snow.
RoleSkin.20205006_Description: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. Its color scheme is rumored to have been inspired by ripe grapes in an orchard.
RoleSkin.20205004_Description: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. Its color scheme is rumored to have been inspired by an upper-class banquet.
RoleSkin.20205003_Description: One of Galatea's many magic costumes. Its color scheme is rumored to have been inspired by a lush bamboo forest.
RoleSkin.20205001_Description: Galatea's magic show outfit is understated yet elegant. To avoid recognition, she wears a wide-brimmed hat—ironically making her even more eye-catching.
RoleSkin.20146206_Description: A knight-style outfit. Beneath its elegant and splendid appearance lies a bold and fierce spirit.
RoleSkin.20146207_Description: A knight-style outfit. Beneath its elegant and splendid appearance lies a bold and fierce spirit.
RoleSkin.20146208_Description: A knight-style outfit. Beneath its elegant and splendid appearance lies a bold and fierce spirit.
RoleSkin.20146209_Description: A knight-style outfit. Beneath its elegant and splendid appearance lies a bold and fierce spirit.
RoleSkin.20146210_Description: A knight-style outfit. Beneath its elegant and splendid appearance lies a bold and fierce spirit.
RoleSkin.20110052_Description: A combat hoodie with a cola print, perfectly matching Bai Mo's vibe. Wearing this outfit, Bai Mo bursts with energy and passion, just like a shaken can of cola.
RoleSkin.20137101_Description:
Kanami wears this stunning gown only for formal events. It blends youthful romance with mature elegance, highlighting her unique brilliance.

"This is the dress I wore when I first took the stage as an idol. I will never forget how I felt back then. I must meet everyone's expectations to feel that kind of emotion again."
RoleSkin.20137054_Description: The cute pink wrapping paper encases the sweet cyan candies. Kanami's outfit perfectly highlights her charming sweetness.
RoleSkin.20105101_Description:
The maid outfit worn by the manager of Café Reminiscence has been tailored to Audrey's liking. Despite the outfit, Audrey's elite leadership aura remains unmistakable.

"Go ahead, take a good look! B-But make sure to try our new coffee... please?"
RoleSkin.20110109_Description:
On the day of the alliance leader election, a flash of green lightning dashes to the crowd, accompanied by loud music. Unlike his usual street dancer slash graffiti artist persona, Bai Mo is dressed to impress, exuding a sense of elegance, though his signature smile of the desire for freedom still lingers.

“If I am re-elected, we'll have 30 days of vacation each month!”

Bai Mo appears surprised as his speech is met with loud applause.

“Wow, you guys are even more enthusiastic than I am!”
RoleSkin.20120053_Description:
During The Scissors' castle exploration, Fragrans, to everyone's surprise, was the fastest to emerge, even with a blindfold on.
"Bats use sound; I use scent... The air outside the castle is indeed much fresher."
RoleSkin.20120054_Description:
After an aquarium trip with her friends, Fragrans made herself a jellyfish-themed outfit.
“Jellyfish... they strike me as light blue flowers blooming on the seabed.”
RoleSkin.20133103_Description:
The outfit Meredith wears while performing for displaced children at a charity event in Preton. Despite her expressionless face, the magician is still adored by the children.

“Magic is but a quantitative technique.”
RoleSkin.20119105_Description:
In a world free of physical ailments, there are healers for the heart. The Scissors are known as radicals. And so, a regular high school girl must still conceal her true "identity."

“Fire purifies. Fire heals all.”
RoleSkin.20131052_Description: An outfit in mysterious purple, featuring images of spider webs, bats, and an ancient castle. Even though this is a fairy tale, Yvette might not necessarily be the princess.
RoleSkin.20109006_Description:
Before the fireflies gathered into a bright moon,
I had never truly seen the moonlight.
RoleSkin.20137109_Description:
Kanami's performance outfit for the Galactic Concert. Songs and battles across the galaxy were once the eternal theme of a sci-fi series. With this outfit, Kanami transforms into a diva singing across the galaxy, expressing her unique interpretation.

'Do you remember the galaxy and love?'
RoleSkin.20112053_Description: The phantom that walks the streets at night is none other than Fuchsia.
RoleSkin.20101056_Description: Upholding fairness and justice is a code every Investigator must follow. Michele is determined to uphold this principle completely.
RoleSkin.20105056_Description:
Walls, turrets, gates—when it comes to classic castle design, that's Audrey's expertise. To assess this property's potential, Audrey donned a brand-new outfit.

"I'm just in need of a horror-themed mansion."
RoleSkin.20146058_Description: The moon rises on a summer night, the grass sways in the wind, and dragonflies flutter. Close your eyes and enjoy this tranquil moment by her side.
RoleSkin.20146102_Description:
The nurse's uniform is angelically pure, but beneath its gentle appearance, there lurks danger.

“You haven't fully recovered. Please stay in bed.”
“Perhaps I should stay a bit longer.”
“...How about forever?”

In her story, she will protect you until the end of time.
RoleSkin.20105001_Description: A mercenary outfit designed by Audrey, integrating her love for glamor into the noble aesthetics inherited from her mother.
RoleSkin.20105051_Description: A personal redesign of Audrey's mercenary outfit, inspired by the hot cocoa coffee she had at noon the day she came up with the design.
RoleSkin.20105010_Description: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Luxurious yet understated, the outfit showcases her resilient will.
RoleSkin.20105009_Description: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Her gaze reaches the vast ocean.
RoleSkin.20105008_Description: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Her gaze reaches the vast ocean.
RoleSkin.20105006_Description: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Secrets flow beneath the simple attire.
RoleSkin.20105002_Description: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. Her unwavering will stands firm like a green mountain.
RoleSkin.20105007_Description: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. A verdant meadow lies within her dreams.
RoleSkin.20105005_Description: A variant of Audrey's mercenary outfit. True elegance needs no lavish adornment.
RoleSkin.20105109_Description:
The outfit Audrey wears to the Spring Blessing family banquet. Featuring the sun on the dress and the moon on the shawl, this elegantly beautiful outfit also exudes the girl's unique charm.

【“Have a seat, ally. You're the Groves' special guest.”】
RoleSkin.20105105_Description:
The outfit Audrey wears while exploring the True Wilderness. Lightweight and comfortable, the outfit lets air through and helps cool the body. The camera in the bag captures visions of the future.

"I must personally inspect the new development areas in collaboration with P.U.S. These photos will witness the rise of a new metropolis."
RoleSkin.20105201_Description: A casual outfit Audrey wears on vacation. Occasionally, she puts this elegant dress on to enjoy her rare holiday with you.
RoleSkin.20105110_Description:
Audrey's custom work outfit. Serious yet fashionable, it is her go-to choice for important occasions. The design has since become popular among office ladies of Neutroville.

“I'm in a hurry - I have another decision to make.”
RoleSkin.20105104_Description:
A Far Eastern garment that was restored by Audrey's costume designer.
It is said that those who pray devoutly while wearing this outfit will obtain mysterious powers to dispel disasters.

“I pray to no one. However... if you were by my side, I’d have the power to dispel any disaster...”
RoleSkin.20107051_Description: She wanders in the red orchard, leaving traces of art on her canvas. By chance, I am drawn to the playful red, lingering on the paths.
RoleSkin.20119106_Description:
Her flames burn hotter than the desert sands. As she moves, ashes rise, heralding an incoming wave of heat.

“One must burn the old shell to gain new strength.”
RoleSkin.20128206_Description: This majestic and elegant attire of a warrior highlights the fearless bravery of the charge into battle. The eye-catching bright red garment resembles a red plum on a cold night, revealing a hint of femininity.
RoleSkin.20128207_Description: This majestic and elegant attire of a warrior highlights the fearless bravery of the charge into battle. The eye-catching bright red garment resembles a red plum on a cold night, revealing a hint of femininity.
