RoleSkin.20107054_Description: This childish blueberry milk outfit suits Maddelena perfectly. After all, only with the heart of a child can one create true beauty.
RoleSkin.20110053_Description: A combat uniform in the style of a spacesuit, not only reflecting Bai Mo's unique personality but also possessing an elegant sense of fantasy.
RoleSkin.20105103_Description: The girl's graceful figure resembles a willow with fine branches, her elegant gauze dress fluttering in the wind. Dressed as a classical dancer, Audrey exudes an indescribable exotic charm with her every move.
RoleSkin.20205054_Description:
Although Galatea is used to being in noisy environments, she occasionally retreats to the peaceful mountains and forests.

“I listen to human voices all the time. Sometimes, I just want to hear what nature has to say.”
RoleSkin.20124051_Description: An engineer-styled combat suit, adorned with playful construction site markings. This outfit is a memento from Kokona's past adventures.
RoleSkin.20108053_Description: The sleek, form-fitting outfit, with an old letter tucked at the waist, gives Nobunaga the appearance of a diligent postman. One wonders, to whom will the most important letter be delivered?
RoleSkin.20128104_Description:
Beneath the flamboyant combat uniform lies Lawine's calm and rational heart. In the shadows, she strikes with lethal precision.

Under the night sky, a shadow races through the city.
No one sees her. No one hears her.
“You let your guard down... playing right into my hands.”
Lawine, the enforcer of The Scissors, strikes again against those who oppose her faith.
RoleSkin.20128056_Description: If you gaze long enough into an abyss, the abyss will gaze back into you. Yet, she remains undeterred.
RoleSkin.20124201_Description: Kokona's loungewear during her vacation. Even at home, she is always ready for the next adventure.
RoleSkin.20124103_Description:
The outfit Kokona wears as a guide at the Space Expericenter, featuring radiation protection, making it suitable for space engineers. The Space Expericenter gave this outfit to Kokona as compensation for her work.

【“Astronaut Kokona out of the spacecraft and reporting for duty. I'm feeling great!”】
RoleSkin.20124053_Description: A modified version of Kokona's combat uniform, incorporating the stripes of a white tiger into the design. Donning this outfit, she appears exceptionally valiant and undeniably dangerous.
RoleSkin.20124105_Description:
The outfit Kokona wears to mountain biking competitions in the fall. Light and durable, it offers excellent breathability and wind resistance reduction and comes equipped with a sufficient tool kit. Rumor has it that Kokona won the championship wearing this outfit.

【“Are you surprised? Great power lies in my body!”】
RoleSkin.20124106_Description:
The formal dress Kokona prepared for the Golden Tree Symphony concert, complete with a cute little hat that highlights her playfulness and anticipation for the challenge.

【“Would you like to try a piano duet? To be a great conductor, one first has to understand the music.”】
RoleSkin.20124104_Description:
A piece of outdoor gear modified by Kokona. Originally intended for exploration, it has been transformed into a ceremonial outfit suitable for outings and picnics. Speaking of which, the strawberries on the outfit seem to be edible.

“If you're interested, feel free to have a bite.”
RoleSkin.20124108_Description: The most romanticized explorer image in Xinxia's mind comes from the popular action-adventure movie series. Xinxia visited old clothing design stores and customized this classic outfit piece by piece. ["Treasures! There are treasures everywhere! Hehe~ But compared to the treasures, I prefer the adventures I encountered along the way!"]
RoleSkin.20124002_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform. The light pink lifts the spirits.
RoleSkin.20124005_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in light purple, resembling the twilight.
RoleSkin.20124007_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in light green, making one feel melancholic.
RoleSkin.20124003_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform. The mix of gray and blue resembles the sky over the mountains.
RoleSkin.20124004_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in azure, resembling the autumn sky.
RoleSkin.20124008_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in red and white, suitable for medical operations.
RoleSkin.20124006_Description: Kokona's spare sniper combat uniform in green camouflage, perfect for stealth operations.
RoleSkin.20131057_Description: A lazy afternoon is best suited for a cup of rich mocha brewed by apprentice barista Yvette.
RoleSkin.20107052_Description: A blue painter's outfit with delicate hand-painted patterns, one of Maddelena's favorites. It sways gracefully, like the shifting starry sky.
RoleSkin.20131108_Description:
Goggles, tactical helmet, combat suit... At the Navigator's invitation, Yvette thoroughly equipped herself with all the gear a tactical analyst needs. Although the battlefield is nothing like the lab, Yvette utilizes her analytical and research skills to support her allies on the front lines.

"T-Tactical Analyst Yvette reporting for duty..."
Her shy, soft voice trembles slightly.
"Um... Navigator, did the combat data I collected help anyone?”
Those gentle, familiar hands softly brush her forehead.
The nervous, blushing girl gradually calms down. The Navigator's reassurance seems to be a magical remedy, empowering her to face anything with courage and resolve.
RoleSkin.20115101_Description:
I invited Flavia to go out with me. To my surprise, she actually said yes.

"Hmm? What's the matter? The weather's lovely, and even butterflies need their sunshine."
RoleSkin.20128106_Description:
The outfit Lawine wears to the Golden Tree Symphony concert. The rebellious design makes her stand out in the classical settings, attracting attention.

【“Music does calm the heart. I do not oppose your invitation.”】
RoleSkin.20128107_Description:
Lawine's fitted model outfit for a performance at Laurel Hall. The elegant, mysterious gown, combined with Lawine's cold demeanor, makes the performance even more enigmatic.

“Target location confirmed. Commencing operation.”
RoleSkin.20128102_Description:
The outfit Lawine wore during a victory celebration for The Scissors. The clash of leather and metal is as punk as it gets. She screams at the world in rebellion.

“Since the world has no future to begin with, why speak of sin?”
RoleSkin.20128105_Description:
Lawine's disguise when she was invited to the Safety Day. Originally intending only to keep an eye on PUS, she was forced to participate in a fairy tale program. Despite Lawine's usual composure, her lifelike ears and tail often seem to betray her thoughts...

【“What do you mean I seem happy?”】
RoleSkin.20128109_Description:
Lawine's maid outfit for working undercover at the café. The red and black tones exude a sense of profound elegance, while the twin daggers hidden behind her add a dangerous touch of beauty.

“The daggers? They're for your protection. Please relax, my dear guest...”
RoleSkin.20128108_Description:
Lawine's special operations combat suit. The camouflage pattern helps her blend seamlessly into the environment, even without using stealth techniques.

“Clear. All areas secured. Victory is ours.”
RoleSkin.20128003_Description: Lawine's spare combat uniform. The cold blue evokes a chill in the heart.
RoleSkin.20128007_Description: Lawine's spare combat uniform in blue, resembling the silent cold night.
RoleSkin.20128004_Description: Lawine's spare combat uniform. The forest green hem looks particularly sleek and neat.
RoleSkin.20128002_Description: Lawine's spare combat uniform. The dazzling gold dust flows like fine sand in the wind.
RoleSkin.20128008_Description: Lawine's spare combat uniform in blue, making her as sharp as thunder on a rainy night.
RoleSkin.20128005_Description: Lawine's spare combat uniform. The beautiful purple showcases her graceful figure.
RoleSkin.20128006_Description: Lawine's spare combat uniform in green, resembling grass fluttering in the wind.
RoleSkin.20128201_Description: The loungewear Lawine dons at home. Only her true friends have a chance to see her in this outfit.
RoleSkin.20124056_Description: Picking up shells, digging for crabs... Wear the summer beach on your body to enjoy the joy of beach treasure hunting at any time.
RoleSkin.20108001_Description: Captain Nobunaga's specialized 1st Division outfit reflects his meticulous approach and disciplined attitude.
RoleSkin.20146056_Description: Celestia's eye-catching green dress sways in the wind, as sweet and cool as a summer breeze. Talking to her while she's wearing it feels refreshing and delightful, like enjoying a cold, sweet drink.
RoleSkin.20132055_Description: Ming's racing outfit incorporates her favorite racing elements. Behind wheels, she turns into a blue whirlwind, becoming the swiftest presence on the track.
RoleSkin.20132106_Description:
Ming's tailored model outfit for a performance at Laurel Hall. To aid her special performance, Ming chose to leave out elaborate decorations, ensuring every inch of the garment is form-fitting.

“If rebellion is the only way to achieve justice, then I don't mind going against the grain.”
RoleSkin.20132107_Description:
Ming's outfit for a night out during Spring Blessing. The striking red dress makes her seem spirited and valiant, embodying the style of a heroine.

【“No, I'm not here to uphold justice, but to enjoy the fine food and drinks!”】
RoleSkin.20132001_Description: Ming's combat suit effortlessly combines practicality and style, making it perfect for both battles and everyday wear.
RoleSkin.20132006_Description: Ming's spare combat suit features an orange-red hue, reminiscent of a sunset's glow.
RoleSkin.20132004_Description: Ming's spare combat uniform. Her heart is as pure as the clear lake in her homeland.
RoleSkin.20132005_Description: Ming's spare combat uniform. Despite her bold character, she does not mind lurking in the dark of the night.
RoleSkin.20132008_Description: Ming's spare combat uniform in purple, resembling the clouds at the edge of the sky.
RoleSkin.20132003_Description: Ming's spare combat uniform in green, resembling the beautiful dream she fights for.
RoleSkin.20132007_Description: Ming's spare combat uniform in blue, symbolizing her lofty aspirations.
RoleSkin.20132002_Description: Ming's spare combat uniform. The bright yellow top makes her as dazzling as the sun.
RoleSkin.20146106_Description:
Celestia's outfit for meteor shower nights combines warmth with style. Its thicker material keeps her cozy while the cute design highlights her simple beauty under the starry sky.

“The beauty of a meteor lies in its fleeting light. Like meteors, we cross the night sky and find each other.”
RoleSkin.20146105_Description:
The outfit Celestia prepared for the amusement park event. The refreshing denim jacket exudes a sense of excitement while the hat perfectly covers her shy eyes when pulled down...

“There are still many attractions left... um, you don't have to look at me, you know?”
RoleSkin.20146109_Description:
Celestia's outfit for hosting the Spring Blessing Eve event at Astral Sanctuary. The decorated skirt does not hide her desire to roam the night with the person dearest to her.

“Would you go for a walk with me after the event? Just the two of us.”
RoleSkin.20146001_Description: Celestia wears this dress while working at Astral Sanctuary. Its twinkling star patterns symbolize Astral Sanctuary's creed of not giving up on any patient.
RoleSkin.20146201_Description: Celestia only puts on this loungewear when resting. Only those closest to her have a chance to see her in this outfit.
RoleSkin.20146104_Description:
An experimental spacesuit Celestia wears at the Space Expericenter. Made from various polymer materials, the outfit offers excellent insulation and impact resistance. Originally designed for interstellar travel, it now resides in the museum for visitors to experience.

“Before stepping into space, we ventured into the fog of dimensions. That's what the tag says.”
RoleSkin.20146006_Description: Celestia's spare work uniform. The leaf-like skirt subtly reveals patterns of stars.
RoleSkin.20146007_Description: Celestia's spare work uniform. The deep blue dress gives her an air of mystery.
RoleSkin.20146011_Description: Celestia's spare work uniform in elegant purple, suitable for formal occasions.
RoleSkin.20146009_Description: Celestia's spare work uniform in navy blue, highlighting her grace.
RoleSkin.20146010_Description: Celestia's spare work uniform in warm orange, reminiscent of lights and delicacies.
RoleSkin.20146005_Description: Celestia's spare work uniform in lime green, accentuating her charm.
RoleSkin.20146008_Description: Celestia's spare work uniform in purple, flowing like a drifting cloud.
RoleSkin.20120052_Description:
Spring is Fragrans' favorite season, full of vitality and renewal.
"Let's make this year's first fragrance a sakura scent."
RoleSkin.20205055_Description:
Who cast the old castle into darkness, and who turned that darkness into a new stage?

“A magician knows more tricks than making doves appear out of thin air. Bats could also do the trick.”
RoleSkin.20112054_Description: The crane ascends into the blue sky, taking hopes and dreams with it.
RoleSkin.20108055_Description: The best investigators are also great drivers, able not only to catch up with criminals in street chases but also to not break the speed limit. How does he do it?
RoleSkin.20128055_Description: As the moon waxes and wanes, people come and go. The only constant is change. An unchanging world is but a reflection of the moon.
RoleSkin.20110055_Description: A casual outfit in refreshing blue and white. Sitting on the beach chair with a cold glass of coconut water in hand, enjoy the vacation as the sea breeze cools you down.
RoleSkin.20112101_Description:
The outfit is inspired by hunters who once roamed the forests at night. Its bizarre design embodies the tension of the era.

“Come on, Fuchsia. You're the only one left! The Nightstalker suits you perfectly!”
“This outfit is not suitable for carrying out missions.”
“Live a little, would you? Come on, it's photo time!”
“Uh... fine.”

Hearing her companions' teasing, Fuchsia remains silent for a while. She knows it's all in fun and that no matter how her outfit changes, her past remains unchanged.
Yet for some reason, she feels a long-lost sense of warmth in her heart.
RoleSkin.20128051_Description: As the maple leaves fall, the interwoven red and white symbolizes Lawine's heart - once beautiful and pure, now tainted by the flames of war.
RoleSkin.20101055_Description: Wearing this pink outfit straight out of a fairy tale, Michele, together with Pawtector, guards the fairy tale kingdom of children's dreams.
RoleSkin.20133051_Description: An outfit prepared by Meredith for aquatic field research. She moves cautiously under the cover of the waves.
RoleSkin.20133106_Description:
Meredith puts on this outfit when performing with her band. The bold design reflects her understanding of the spirit of rock n' roll. A composed scholar, Meredith also longs for freedom without restraints.

“Rock n' roll embodies freedom and exploration, aligning perfectly with the spirit of science.”
RoleSkin.20133003_Description: Meredith's spare combat uniform, featuring her familiar colors. Perhaps, deep inside her, there is a blueprint of the future.
RoleSkin.20133006_Description: Meredith's spare combat uniform in red, matching the color of The Scissors. The rusty blade of yesteryear shall hew an iron path.
RoleSkin.20133004_Description: Meredith's spare combat uniform. Its gray-brown color evokes the scorching desert sands, with shadows growing deeper as the sun blazes brighter.
RoleSkin.20133007_Description: Meredith's spare combat uniform. Its deep green color resembles ancient trees, blossoming with new buds after a long slumber.
RoleSkin.20133002_Description: Meredith's spare combat uniform in purple, resembling litmus paper. Using herself as a measure, she gauges the balance of the world.
RoleSkin.20133008_Description: Meredith's spare combat uniform in light green, resembling the tender buds of spring. A new hope needs nurturing and care.
RoleSkin.20133005_Description: Meredith's spare combat uniform. Its deep verdigris color symbolizes the beginning of change.
RoleSkin.20146101_Description:
A dreamlike dress with a resplendently complex design, seemingly inspired by a famous fairy tale.

【“What's in the world of dreams?”
“A queen, tea parties, and pretty dresses?”
“What else?”
“And the navigating Rabbit-sen... No, Mr. Rabbit!”
People think that her dreams linger in fairy tales, filled only with baseless beauty and fantasy.
Yet, there are also memories of certain real people.】
RoleSkin.20124102_Description:
Inspired by flight suits from old movies, this outfit embodies Kokona's unfulfilled dreams. Ever curious about the world since childhood, she has always longed for the sky and distant lands, wishing to discover unknown territories.

“Let's see. This is the center stick, and that is the altimeter... Relax. I've read the manual dozens of times. Remember where to pull to activate the ejection seat. We're taking off!”
RoleSkin.20101206_Description: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
RoleSkin.20101207_Description: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
RoleSkin.20101208_Description: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
RoleSkin.20101209_Description: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
RoleSkin.20101210_Description: A special operations outfit provided by P.U.S, remodeled from Michele's father's combat uniform. The mighty white tiger strikes fear into the hearts of all criminals.
RoleSkin.20101053_Description: Whenever the P.U.S roads are blocked due to weather, Michele never hesitates to take action. Clad in waterproof gear and armed with warning signs, she becomes a striking figure in the rain.
RoleSkin.20101052_Description: Michele wears this outfit whenever there are holiday festivities. The vibrant colors and festive pattern put a joyful spirit in the air!
RoleSkin.20132103_Description:
The beach and the waves, music and dancing—it's the perfect retreat for a warrior like Ming. A brief moment of joy prepares her for fiercer battles ahead.

"This beach isn't half bad. Finally, a chance to relax." As she arrives, Ming reveals a rare smile. "Tonight, we sing and celebrate! Tomorrow, we fight as one!"

Who knows how many companions she'll outdrink tonight...
RoleSkin.20112052_Description: The act of protecting lives is the only thing more noble than life itself.
RoleSkin.20128052_Description: The elegant outfit resembles an ancient scroll of majestic mountains. The classical attire reflects Lawine's beautiful yet cold demeanor.
RoleSkin.20131055_Description: A pale pink lab coat adorned with cherry blossoms, snowy mountains, and a bright moon, as if Yvette stands in the wind with petals gently landing on her shoulders.
RoleSkin.20109054_Description: The light blue denim jacket is full of vitality and passion, creating a sharp contrast with Reiichi's indifferent expression. Beneath his cold demeanor, powerful energy surges.
RoleSkin.20107103_Description:
The beautiful seaside inspires the young painter. The refreshing sailor suit makes her even more charming.

【The azure sea, the white waves, and the singing crowd; Maddelena is intoxicated by the beautiful scene.
Taking out the paintbrush she carries with her at all times, she expresses her emotions onto the canvas.
After a while, a sudden idea comes to her:
Deep in everyone's heart, there is an ocean unique to them.】
RoleSkin.20137053_Description: This elegant mint-colored outfit makes Kanami appear even more pure and charming, adding a touch of coolness to the passionate summer concert.
RoleSkin.20112055_Description: Games can sometimes be deadly. At least, she believes so.
RoleSkin.20105052_Description: Audrey puts on this cute dress whenever she strolls along the beach. Only then does she reveal her tender side.
RoleSkin.20115104_Description:
Wearing a vibrant and elegant restaurant uniform, Flavia seamlessly blends into a street-side café. Under the beautiful sunset, Flavia and the guests savor Iberian delicacies as much as the romantic atmosphere.

"At sunset, I serve them jamón ibérico and all its rich flavors."
RoleSkin.20107105_Description:
Maddelena's outfit for flash mob performances. Ever since the Golden Tree Symphony event, her love for music seems to have been awakened, albeit not for classical music...

【“Melodies exist only for a moment before vanishing. Don't you find it romantic?”】
RoleSkin.20107110_Description:
Maddelena prepared this outfit for the amusement park event. Its cute design blends seamlessly with the park's cartoon characters.

【“I'm only dressed like this to better understand children's feelings... After all, I get commissioned to create children's picture books from time to time.”】
RoleSkin.20107106_Description:
The outfit Maddelena wears to the Golden Tree Symphony concert. Designed by herself, the outfit features a small hat that helps hide her shy face.

【“I must not embarrass myself during the concert!”】
RoleSkin.20107007_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The interwoven silver and red make her stand out from the crowd.
RoleSkin.20107010_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit, incredibly clear like a lake in winter.
RoleSkin.20107011_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit, modest and serene like leaves of fall.
RoleSkin.20107002_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The bright green symbolizes vitality and vigor.
RoleSkin.20107004_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The deep indigo symbolizes creativity and intuition.
RoleSkin.20107003_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The tender pink resembles butterflies and blooming flowers.
RoleSkin.20107009_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The interwoven blue and green resemble ripples in a lake.
RoleSkin.20107008_Description: A special variant of Maddelena's painter's outfit. The noble purple makes her seem like a flower swaying in the wind.
RoleSkin.20107102_Description:
Wearing this outfit, Maddelena appears sweet and energetic, like a dazzling neon light weaving through the streets. As an artist, she occasionally indulges in the extraordinary.

"Hiya! Good evening! Woo!"
With a face full of excitement, she glides by on her roller skates.
Her elegant figure and the flickering rainbow lights dazzle onlookers.
Whatever this whimsical girl does, it is always in the name of "gathering inspiration."
RoleSkin.20107108_Description:
Maddelena designed this vibrant classic dress after doing a lot of research. When she dances, tambourines ring with her every move, reflecting the romantic charm of a bygone era.

“I initially just needed some inspiration, but now I've completely fallen in love with the dance!”
RoleSkin.20107201_Description: Loungewear designed by Maddelena, inspired by the green fields and orange fruit. Coming up with fun designs at home with you is the precious time she cherishes the most.
RoleSkin.20107055_Description:
A traveling outfit designed by Maddelena.
On the Ferris wheel in the amusement park, the girl in light pink watches the fireworks lighting up the sky, treasuring this unique form of inspiration.
RoleSkin.20107053_Description: Donning a simple and practical outfit, Maddelena embarks on a journey alone, resembling a courier on an urgent delivery. Only then does she realize that the world is much larger than she imagined.
RoleSkin.20120005_Description: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat. Its deep rose color highlights her mature elegance.
RoleSkin.20120002_Description: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat, in a refreshing green reminiscent of freshly sprouted tea leaves.
RoleSkin.20120006_Description: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat, with tones reminiscent of autumn leaves, foreshadowing winter's arrival.
RoleSkin.20120004_Description: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat. The violet blooms in the night, as intoxicating as fine wine.
RoleSkin.20120007_Description: An alternative color scheme for Fragrans' lab coat, where blue symbolizes not just melancholy, but also inner peace.
RoleSkin.20120003_Description: An alternative color scheme of Fragrans' lab coat, featuring a purity akin to refined essence.
RoleSkin.20120055_Description: The outfit Fragrans wore when visiting the Sea of Blossoms. On that snowy day, plum blossoms bloomed on the corners of her fluttering clothes, covering her in their faint scent.
RoleSkin.20120102_Description:
Fragrans' medical attire, whether she's accustomed to it or not, serves the same purpose: to heal and soothe.

“It's important for you to rest well.”
RoleSkin.20120001_Description: Fragrans' smart and elegant lab coat is exactly what you'd expect from a person with such a scholarly temperament.
RoleSkin.20133001_Description: A special combat uniform crafted with the cutting-edge technology of The Scissors, incorporating Meredith's lifetime of knowledge into its complex design.
RoleSkin.20110101_Description:
A baker's uniform designed by Bai Mo, featuring an avant-garde design and comfortable lining. However, he has rarely had the chance to put it on.

【“Look. This blueberry milk bread is golden on the outside with a soft and fluffy texture and a sweet and sour taste. I baked it myself. ”
Bai Mo once worked undercover in one of his bakeries for several days.
Seeing people enjoy the bread he has baked fills his heart with joy.
To this day, that remains one of his fondest memories.】
RoleSkin.20110001_Description: Bai Mo wears this mercenary outfit when he is out on missions. The design emphasizes practicality while incorporating streetwear elements - sleek, carefree, unfettered.
RoleSkin.20110056_Description: Bai Mo's barista outfit is rumored to be from when he secretly worked at a cafe in Urbino for half a month.
RoleSkin.20110007_Description: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit. He has battled waves and dived into the depths of the sea.
RoleSkin.20110002_Description: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit makes him look like a young boy about to enjoy a picnic.
RoleSkin.20110005_Description: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit, resembling the vast green fields in his childhood dreams.
RoleSkin.20110006_Description: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit, resembling the autumn leaves that dance in the wind of freedom.
RoleSkin.20110004_Description: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit, bold yet romantic and elegant.
RoleSkin.20110008_Description: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit. In the sea of sand, the voice of freedom will stir a new storm.
RoleSkin.20110003_Description: Bai Mo's spare mercenary outfit in elegant lake blue reflects his unrestrained spirit.
RoleSkin.20110106_Description:
A performance suit customized by the Bai Group. Donning this outfit, Bai Mo exudes a calm and dignified aura; that is until he speaks...

【“My pitch isn't half bad, right?”】
RoleSkin.20108054_Description: The white shirt paired with a brown jacket and tie gives Nobunaga an air of elegance and unattainability, making him smell of aromatic coffee beans.
RoleSkin.20131056_Description: Under the simple white and blue coat, Yvette's orange socks evoke the sweetness of soda. Though usually introverted and shy, Yvette occasionally shows this sweet side.
RoleSkin.20132052_Description: With a green top resembling leaves and orange-yellow bottoms resembling flowers, Ming is dressed like a coltsfoot, symbolizing freedom. She vows that hunger and oppression will end, and coltsfoot flowers will bloom again on this land.
RoleSkin.20107001_Description: A simple yet artistic painter's outfit. Rather than elaborate attire, Maddelena cares more about the harmony of colors.
RoleSkin.20101112_Description:
Michele's outfit for the Spring Blessing fireworks celebration. The bright dress reflects the festive atmosphere while the jingling gold bells herald the arrival of spring.

【“Ding-dong! What are you waiting for? The fireworks celebration is about to start!”】
RoleSkin.20101113_Description:
Michele wore this outfit when invited as a volunteer representative to a pool party. To fully enjoy the pool, she styled her hair into a neat, cute braid and paired it with pineapple sunglasses.

“Doing good deeds has finally paid off. I got invited to a pool party! I, the gaming master, will take you all down in the water gun battle!”
RoleSkin.20101109_Description:
Michele's ski suit for the Winter Wilderness Challenge. A thick cotton jacket with a snow leopard-patterned fur trim, highlighting her cuteness as well as her zest for life.

“Come on. Can you keep up?”
RoleSkin.20101106_Description:
Michele's work uniform at the candy shop. The newly opened amusement park is bustling. In order to prevent accidents, Michele volunteers to work undercover at the park's candy shop.
A member of The Scissors suddenly appears in the crowd, putting Michele on high alert. As they lock eyes briefly, they tacitly decide to ignore one another, for they both see a smile of joy on the other party's face.

【If this is a fleeting dream, I hope I never have to wake up.】
RoleSkin.20101001_Description: Michele incorporates her favorite cat elements into her uniform, giving it a playful touch while maintaining the professionalism expected of a P.U.S investigator.
RoleSkin.20101011_Description: Michele's spare investigator uniform. Its industrial style conveys a sense of reliability and practicality.
RoleSkin.20101008_Description: Michele's investigator uniform. Lightly dyed in khaki, it is simple and durable.
RoleSkin.20101009_Description: Michele's spare investigator uniform in a bright, spritely pink.
RoleSkin.20101012_Description: Michele's investigator uniform. The light gray-blue makes the wearer appear calm and collected.
RoleSkin.20101006_Description: Michele's investigator uniform in a minty fresh blue.
RoleSkin.20101007_Description: Michele's spare investigator uniform in a lively spring green.
RoleSkin.20101010_Description: Michele's spare investigator uniform in a mysterious, ethereal purple.
RoleSkin.20101201_Description: Michele's carefully matched casual outfit, sharing the more pleasant meow time with you.
RoleSkin.20132104_Description:
A rugged cowboy outfit that embodies a maverick's longing for freedom and adventure. Thinking of this, Ming whistles cheerfully.

“Let's pull off a big score!”
RoleSkin.20146053_Description: The candies adorn the dress with rainbow colors as her aura blooms in the summer. What color will the next rainbow candy be?
RoleSkin.20108102_Description:
The tight swimwear and beach shorts, though simple, showcase Nobunaga's outstanding temperament. During his brief rest, Nobunaga wants to be left alone, feeling the sea breeze blowing on his face.

【During his joyful seaside vacation, Nobunaga lies alone on a beach chair, looking at the sky.
Is something on his mind? Has something happened? Nobunaga denies.
“I'm just contemplating my future and value.”
“Stay with me for a while, would you? Perhaps I'd be more determined when you're with me.”】
RoleSkin.20105055_Description: The clash of black tea and cherry blossoms creates a unique springtime flair. When Audrey dons this outfit, her mood seems to lighten with the season.
RoleSkin.20115102_Description:
A luxurious and elegant maid outfit inspired by butterflies. Donning this enhancing outfit, Flavia mysteriously appears in the café. She seems to have obtained important intel about someone.

“Are you looking to trade information? You'll have to defeat me first.”
RoleSkin.20124055_Description: An elegant outfit featuring patterns of snowflakes and pine trees, looking even more graceful on Kokona. She may be the only one who knows the true meaning behind it.
RoleSkin.20112102_Description:
Fuchsia's assassination suit for urban combat, combining practicality and mobility with her personal aesthetics. The shark-fin aerodynamic panels further aid in gliding. Donning this outfit, she becomes a shadow darting between buildings, speaking via the sound of gunfire.

【“Bang! A quick and clean end. That's all.”】
RoleSkin.20112105_Description:
A maid outfit designed by Fuchsia, integrating her understanding of maids' work. It is lightweight and tight-fitting, allowing Fuchsia to display her powerful and efficient combat abilities.

“If you don't want to end up on the declutter list... then don't get in the way.”
RoleSkin.20112056_Description: Fuchsia's disguise as a café employee. Sharks might not like coffee, but the rich aroma of caramel coffee adds a touch of warmth to her frosty demeanor.
RoleSkin.20112103_Description:
Fuchsia's outfit during the first Champion of Relaxation competition. Lightweight, comfortable, and cool, the outfit features brown and green tones that allow her to blend into her surroundings as she treks through rivers and mountains.

“Thanks to my outfit, I could sneak up on animals without being noticed... An interesting experience.”
RoleSkin.20112104_Description:
The outfit Fuchsia wore to the holiday parade. Originally intended to help her keep a low profile while protecting VIPs, its attention-grabbing design unexpectedly made her the star of the parade.

“What a noisy bunch.”
RoleSkin.20112106_Description:
Fuchsia wears this outfit when she works as a bartender in the underground bar. Watching her expert moves, one can't help but ask,

"Why are you so skilled at this?!"

"It's nothing out of the ordinary. I just like to be the best in every field, bartending included. Would you like a drink?"
RoleSkin.20112206_Description: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
RoleSkin.20112207_Description: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
RoleSkin.20112208_Description: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
RoleSkin.20112209_Description: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
RoleSkin.20112210_Description: Fuchsia's diving suit for a special mission is designed after a shark's anatomy, making her resemble a deep-sea predator. The suit features a tail fin from a recently deceased shark, and her mission seems to involve getting close to its companions.
RoleSkin.20112007_Description: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform. May all who walk upon this earth be free.
RoleSkin.20112006_Description: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform. Aren't humans just another type of fish?
RoleSkin.20112003_Description: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform. The eye-catching red signifies the heat of the muzzle.
RoleSkin.20112002_Description: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform, cold as ice, sharp as a killer.
RoleSkin.20112005_Description: Fuchsia's spare combat suit: Purple isn't just mysterious, it can also be deadly.
RoleSkin.20112008_Description: Fuchsia's spare combat uniform. Stealth is not just about concealing one's presence.
RoleSkin.20112004_Description: Fuchsia's spare combat suit, designed for twilight—the witching hour, when demons emerge, ready to devour.
RoleSkin.20112057_Description: Fuchsia's athletic outfit features a striking mix of pink shark and teal iceberg, creating a unique visual impact.
RoleSkin.20146054_Description: Donning this gilded teal dress, Celestia looks like a gorgeous princess. Be careful not to touch her, for the thorns are prickly.
RoleSkin.20112001_Description: A professional assassin's tight suit. Born for battle, its streamlined design is devoid of any superfluous elements.
RoleSkin.20119101_Description:
Eika’s self-styled outdoor gear showcases bold and edgy fashion that embodies the wild spirit of a high school girl. Exactly where she "lets loose" after school is her little secret.

“The day of a high school student only begins after school!”
RoleSkin.20119055_Description: Eika's uniform for her farm job. Based on a basic work uniform, it blends elements of meadow green and earthy tones. Her cheerful presence is a hit at the farm, even attracting the farm's robotic herding dog. Are they playing a friendly game... or is Eika simply afraid of dogs?
RoleSkin.20119052_Description: Eika's outfit for her café job, inspired by the "Manager's Daily Coffee Pick." As both a barista and model, Eika often prepares coffee for customers herself. Her sales figures are said to be impressive.
RoleSkin.20119102_Description:
Eika put together this outfit for her side job at the planetarium, blending elements from sci-fi movies with a girl's dreamy imagination of the stars. While working inside the planetarium, Eika realizes that being a galactic courier could be the coolest job ever.

"If our family restaurant spanned the universe, would I have to deliver food among planets?"
RoleSkin.20119053_Description: Eika's fast food uniform. This unique combo of a school and staff attire, helps her look the part and complements her youthful style. Rumor is that the dripping red feature was inspired by Eika's mournful experience of accidentally spilling chili sauce all over a big plate of chicken nuggets.
RoleSkin.20119051_Description: The outfit Eika wears while working at a fashion store, blending uniform style with trending pink and dark city designs. As an in-store model, Eika often showcases these outfits herself, reportedly boosting sales impressively.
RoleSkin.20119054_Description: Eika wears this uniform when working part-time at the game store. It's accented with the color scheme of a popular gaming console. Promoting games is part of the job, so Eika often competes with pro gamers. It's become quite the attraction.
RoleSkin.20119005_Description: Eika’s winter uniform. Breathe in the cold air and gaze at the clear blue sky.
RoleSkin.20119002_Description: Eika's summer edition uniform. Perfect for napping among the dense trees and grass.
RoleSkin.20119008_Description: Eika's early spring uniform. As the winter snow melts, green sprouts once more.
RoleSkin.20119003_Description: Eika's spring edition uniform. Rushing to campus amidst a flurry of petals and pollen.
RoleSkin.20119004_Description: Eika's fall edition uniform. Amidst the falling leaves, she savors the aroma of roasted sweet potatoes.
RoleSkin.20119006_Description: Eika's worn-out uniform. It has been worn and washed many times, but she still cherishes it.
RoleSkin.20119007_Description: Eika’s taro colored uniform. To be honest, it only turned purple after being put in the wrong wash basket.
RoleSkin.20119001_Description: Eika's school uniform is the most common style in the Preton region. However, due to Eika's high body temperature, she has specially modified it with ventilation openings.
RoleSkin.20115052_Description: Flavia's formal attire for the P.U.S award ceremony. She won't stop there; she'll keep climbing until no one is left to bestow honors upon her.
RoleSkin.20115054_Description: Flavia's customized outfit. The viper lurks in the water, waiting for its thirsty prey. No, she is not the viper; she is the hunter waiting next to it.
RoleSkin.20115053_Description: Flavia's custom lavender outfit. Its subtle fragrance lulls you to sleep amidst the dance of butterflies.
RoleSkin.20115051_Description: Flavia's custom outfit, inspired by coffee, milk, and cream. Walking the line between coffee and milk is a dangerous game.
RoleSkin.20115001_Description: Flavia's combat uniform features a simple and comfortable design. Butterfly elements add a final touch, highlighting the wearer's elegant charm.
RoleSkin.20115007_Description: Flavia's spare uniform. A dim flame that has lost its warmth burns coldly like a phantom.
RoleSkin.20115003_Description: Flavia's spare uniform, resembling an unfathomable deep lake.
RoleSkin.20115004_Description: Flavia's spare uniform. The bud that has endured the cold winter waits for spring to bloom.
RoleSkin.20115005_Description: Flavia's spare uniform. The butterfly folds its wings, hiding among the decayed leaves.
RoleSkin.20115002_Description: Flavia's spare uniform. Butterfly wings flutter with the breeze, teasingly drifting near and far, always just out of reach.
RoleSkin.20115006_Description: Flavia's spare uniform. Lies and truth become indistinguishable, blending into the purple night.
RoleSkin.20101107_Description:
A blue and white navy uniform equipped with a communication device and a cute survival backpack tailored to Michele's fighting style.
Facing the sea breeze, Michele appears more spirited than usual.

"Anchors aweigh! Hope you don't get seasick~"
RoleSkin.20108051_Description: The black and blue electronic-style outfit, featuring a walkie-talkie emblazoned with a record pattern, adds a touch of fashion to the typically stoic Nobunaga.
RoleSkin.20124101_Description:
A fun outfit for the concert of Duckyucky, the virtual idol. With a cute avant-garde design, this limited outfit is treasured by Kokona.

"Are you ready, Kokona? Duckyucky's concert is about to start!"
"Of course... Oh no!"
"W-What's going on? What was that noise...?"
"Something's happening! Emergency mission!"
And so, the girl, dressed in her fun outfit, rushes to the front line.
RoleSkin.20205051_Description:
Although Galatea prefers drinks “stronger” than coffee, she admits that these coffee beans do have a unique flavor.

“Hmm... Next time, I'll add some liquor and make spiked Sidra coffee.”
RoleSkin.20128054_Description: The record player imagery on the outfit seems to constantly play melodies of the past, occasionally stirring Lawine's memories of bygone times.
RoleSkin.20132054_Description: A brisk outdoor outfit decorated with antler emblems. Ming often dons it when wandering in the wilderness, recalling her vibrant homeland while igniting a new fighting spirit.
RoleSkin.20120103_Description:
Fragrans follows the map in search of mythic ingredients in the Cosmite desert. She has changed into a cooler outfit to endure the scorching heat.

“Follow the scent. You can't read maps with a blindfold on.”
RoleSkin.20109055_Description: As a sniper, Reiichi has also participated in frontal assaults. Dressed in jungle-style attire, he is brave and ruthless, always managing to remain patient until the mission starts.
RoleSkin.20132051_Description: Dressed in a white, red, and gold combat uniform, Ming resembles a messenger calling upon holy fire to punish the wicked. Shoot and burn until true dawn arrives.
RoleSkin.20110103_Description:
A futuristic sports outfit with bright colors and a sleek design. Bai Mo has infused it with his own unique touches.

“Oh, you caught me! Are you here to take me back as well?”
Although cornered, Bai Mo still bears a cunning smile.
“I'm not slacking off. The leader of Urbino must be free. Locking me in an office would be a huge waste.”
As you're drawn in by his words, he leaps away, skillfully escaping your view with expert parkour.
RoleSkin.20119103_Description:
The summer sea is unlikely to remain calm, as the brilliant luster of spark fish takes center stage. Through fire and passion, they ignite a glorious storm beneath the waves.

“I can show you a sight - the seabed dyed red by hot winds.”
RoleSkin.20109056_Description: This outfit, adorned with crossed swords, resembles an ancient pirate captain's attire. Reiichi does not fear the curse of the sea, for he has long cursed himself.
RoleSkin.20137052_Description: A performance costume featuring a shooting star pattern. The fluttering starlight resembles Kanami's gorgeous dance moves.
RoleSkin.20132101_Description:
A black outfit designed for nighttime operations. Originally meant to blend seamlessly into the dark, Ming insisted on adding a touch of dark red, like a quietly burning flame—subtle yet unyielding. She will chase the night and drive it away.

“Go home, kids. The night is my battlefield.”
RoleSkin.20128001_Description: A special ops suit compatible with The Scissors' optical camouflage technology. Efficient and practical, it was designed specifically for Lawine.
RoleSkin.20107056_Description: Trying to figure out how to express feelings through creation, Maddelena takes a part-time job as a courier. She believes that letters are an important medium to convey one's intentions. She has designed her backpack in the shape of a mailbox, inviting the delivery of any precious sentiments.
RoleSkin.20101054_Description: Michele occasionally puts on this casual outfit and goes hiking in her free time. Be careful not to mistake her for a wildcat in the bamboo forest.
RoleSkin.20112110_Description:
Aside from a well-stocked arsenal, victory in battle also relies on meticulous strategies and overwhelming firepower. Fuchsia knows this well, as is evident by her Shark Squad's domination in live-action shooter games.

“If you're my eyes of an eagle, Navigator, then I am your teeth of a shark. Let's win this, as we always do!”
RoleSkin.20109053_Description: In his crisp white attire, Reiichi looks like a young doctor. But in reality, he's only skilled in battlefield emergency care.
RoleSkin.20110051_Description: A chef's outfit featuring patterns of fish and bamboo leaves, reminiscent of the aroma of sushi. To Bai Mo, freedom and delicacies are the two most important things in life.
RoleSkin.20137104_Description:
The outfit Kanami wore when she performed in a rural concert. The mud on her light dungarees skirt does not ruin her cute style. Kanami chose to keep this outfit after the show ended.

“There's something so satisfying about watching the crops grow day by day.”
RoleSkin.20137108_Description:
Kanami's costume for her mythological play. Inspired by a Greek goddess, the dress resembles pure ocean waves with a skirt shaped like a mermaid's tail, topped with a golden laurel for a touch of sanctity.

“I will pray for you. Always.” The girl pours all her emotions and thoughts into the final line. “Rehearsing with you really does... Uh, never mind.”

The girl hesitates for a moment before deciding not to finish her sentence.
RoleSkin.20137055_Description: Kanami's promotional outfit for the coffee brand was inspired by latte art, designed to convey a warm, coffee-like sentiment to her fans.
RoleSkin.20137106_Description:
Kanami wore this dress, which borrows elements from the tuxedo and the tutu, for the magic show that she was invited to perform in at Laurel Hall. Elegance and romance are Kanami's eternal pursuits, and there seems to be a hidden mystery in the gorgeous ornaments on the skirt.

"Phew... You can do it, Kanami. We must get our things back!"
RoleSkin.20137105_Description:
The outfit Kanami wears when invited to the Golden Tree Symphony concert. It highlights her charm and coordination with the conductor. Intentional, perhaps?

“I would like to dream the most beautiful dream with you.”
RoleSkin.20137103_Description:
Kanami's choice of loungewear while on vacation. Few realize that under the spotlight, the invincible idol is just an ordinary girl offstage, entitled to enjoy her youthful moments.
However, as an idol, she is always keenly aware of others' gazes, making her feel a tad nervous and excited, holding onto the person standing next to her.

【Lup-dup... Do you hear Kanami's heartbeat?】
RoleSkin.20137056_Description: Kanami's special edition costume is inspired by a sunflower field under the bright sun, showcasing Kanami's boundless ardor.
RoleSkin.20137051_Description: Kanami's special performance costume, with a charming yet slightly dangerous aura. Perhaps she will appear in your dreams tonight.
RoleSkin.20137006_Description: Kanami's spare performance costume, as elegant as a phoenix and as subtle as a dragon's whisper.
RoleSkin.20137005_Description: Kanami's spare performance costume. The nightingale's song lingers in the endless night.
RoleSkin.20137004_Description: Kanami's spare performance costume in brilliant violet, blooming to its fullest.
RoleSkin.20137003_Description: Kanami's spare performance outfit, in dazzling orange and yellow, mirrors the passionate flames in her heart.
RoleSkin.20137007_Description: Kanami's spare performance costume. The gilded color reflects the idol's radiance.
RoleSkin.20137002_Description: Kanami's spare performance costume in cyan, resembling delicate petals.
RoleSkin.20137008_Description: Kanami's spare performance costume in green, symbolizing growth.
RoleSkin.20137001_Description: Kanami's performance outfit is both beautiful and practical. Its slender, flowing design resembles a nightingale spreading its wings.
RoleSkin.20108052_Description: The elegant outfit, embroidered with thorns and a sword, symbolizes Nobunaga's turbulent fate and his fearless resolve to confront hardships.
RoleSkin.20133052_Description: With a striking mix of black and white, which side truly represents her? Meredith is as enigmatic as this outfit.
RoleSkin.20128053_Description: The black and red hues symbolize the calamity that befell her hometown. Lawine is determined to give it her all to prevent history from repeating itself.
RoleSkin.20132102_Description:
A tight combat uniform in black and red that blends high-tech and retro aesthetics. Her cool and tough facade does little to hide the burning heat deep in her soul.

“Don't make a mess. I don't have time to clean up after you.”
“Listen to me if you want to live! Understood?”
Under Ming's command, each attack is as sharp as a scalpel.
But she fights not for distant ideals, but for survival and the wrath deep within her.
RoleSkin.20110054_Description: A racing driver-style combat uniform in black and green, making Bai Mo appear dashing and distinctive. Speed and passion perfectly describe Bai Mo.
RoleSkin.20132053_Description: A combat uniform in black and blue, decorated with lightning and eagle emblems. Ming's eyes are as sharp as a hawk's. The outfit highlights her dangerously intimidating aura.

RoleTeam.3_TeamDesc: These Strinovian from all walks of life have banded together to fight for their "own ideals."
RoleTeam.2_TeamDesc: Active in all parts of Strinova society, this mysterious organization is not to be underestimated. They are wary of the changes in Strinova and hold a deep suspicion toward "Utopia."
RoleTeam.1_TeamDesc: Led by Sistine and made up of veteran agents and talented newcomers, PUS is dedicated to protecting the order and security of "Utopia."

RoleVoice.22121140_Content: MVP? Obviously! I have you to thank for my brilliant performance.
RoleVoice.22132079_Content: All injustice will perish in gunfire!
RoleVoice.22137068_Content: The preparations are complete. My performance is about to begin!
RoleVoice.22110139_Content: Just a temporary setback... Let's try again.
RoleVoice.22115139_Content: One careless move loses the whole game.
RoleVoice.22101069_Content: Fight with me, and justice will be ours!
RoleVoice.22205081_Content: Let's go stir up some fun~
RoleVoice.22109067_Content: Let's lead the revolution of this world together.
RoleVoice.22133137_Content:
Next time, I won't forgive such failure.
Do your best.
RoleVoice.22146137_Content: I won't let this happen again.
RoleVoice.22115073_Content: If you want to avoid being charmed, you have to do more than just closing your eyes.
RoleVoice.22128112_Content: Do not sink into the darkness!
RoleVoice.22119112_Content: Don't stop Eika! Did I say that right?
RoleVoice.22108139_Content: Get out of your comfort zone. To fail is to learn.
RoleVoice.22120138_Content: The flowers bloom no matter the weather.
RoleVoice.22124138_Content: Good job. This victory was a team effort.
RoleVoice.22128113_Content: This world isn't yours to take!
RoleVoice.22119067_Content: I will protect you whenever you need me.
RoleVoice.22109073_VoiceName: Active skill: Light screen, blind them!
RoleVoice.22109073_VoiceNameShort: Active skill: Light screen, blind them!
RoleVoice.22131072_VoiceName: Active Skill: It's Up to You
RoleVoice.22131072_VoiceNameShort: Active Skill: It's Up to You
RoleVoice.22205073_VoiceName: Active Skill: Another Side of Me
RoleVoice.22205073_VoiceNameShort: Active Skill: Another Side of Me
RoleVoice.22108074_VoiceName: Active Skill: Leave It to Me
RoleVoice.22108074_VoiceNameShort: Active Skill: Leave It to Me
RoleVoice.22120074_VoiceName: Active Skill: Give it a Try
RoleVoice.22120074_VoiceNameShort: Active Skill: Give it a Try
RoleVoice.22120083_Content: Maybe it's time to fall back.
RoleVoice.22107137_Content: I gave it my all, you know...
RoleVoice.22146066_Content: I'll always be here if you need me.
RoleVoice.22205137_Content: Today, the rhythm of the performance eluded me.
RoleVoice.22132067_Content: Even if I die today, I'll do so with no regrets.
RoleVoice.22137073_Content: Listen closely, there will be echoes.
RoleVoice.22108112_Content: You won't get away with it!
RoleVoice.22121067_Content: But I will grow stronger until I break the chains!
RoleVoice.22121070_Content: Are you all ready to face the challenge?
RoleVoice.22128074_Content: There is no escape for you.
RoleVoice.22107109_Content: You let your guard down, huh!
RoleVoice.22110069_Content: Urbino has everything you desire, including liberty!
RoleVoice.22115077_Content: Can you guess which one of me is real?
RoleVoice.22120111_Content: Your scent will be covered by the fragrance.
RoleVoice.22107114_Content: You don't look so tough, do you?
RoleVoice.22205020_Content: Curious about where I've hidden it? Well, that's the allure of a magician's secret.
RoleVoice.22105137_Content: Just you wait. I won't lose next time.
RoleVoice.22112020_Content: Not bad to use it occasionally.
RoleVoice.22205111_Content: As easy as slicing through petals.
RoleVoice.22131114_Content: Try as you might, the outcome remains the same.
RoleVoice.22119113_VoiceName: Elimination: Time for a New Outfit
RoleVoice.22119113_VoiceNameShort: Elimination: Time for a New Outfit
RoleVoice.22998018_Content: Defeat the final opponent with Kanami!
RoleVoice.22105079_Content: You will not escape the flames!
RoleVoice.22108129_Content: Don't worry. I will protect you.
RoleVoice.22115079_Content: Don't blink, lest you miss it.
RoleVoice.22115069_Content: To set the rules, one must first know the rules.
RoleVoice.22120020_Content: I would like some advice on secondary weapons.
RoleVoice.22101067_Content: I will uphold the order of Strinova!
RoleVoice.22128139_Content: Was my best shot... just not enough?
RoleVoice.22205067_Content: They belong only to you and me.
RoleVoice.22205139_Content: As long as the audience enjoys a splendid show, the act is never a failure.
RoleVoice.22110068_Content: As long as I'm still breathing, no one shall control Urbino!
RoleVoice.22121068_Content: We just need to win this battle, right? I'll play by the rules.
RoleVoice.22105129_Content: I've saved you. Don't you forget it.
RoleVoice.22101137_Content: Damn it... I shouldn't have lost!
RoleVoice.22110137_Content: Damn it. I was this close!
RoleVoice.22115138_Content: A pleasure working with you, Navigator.
RoleVoice.22137066_Content: Listen up—The battlefield is my stage!
RoleVoice.22121138_Content: Phew! I won. Told you I was good.
RoleVoice.22120140_Content: Did I overdo it? Maybe the aroma was a bit too potent...
RoleVoice.22121066_Content: One cannot escape from the shackles of destiny...
RoleVoice.22112068_Content: Same as always, just complete the task.
RoleVoice.22101140_Content: Haha, I knew I could do it!
RoleVoice.22124137_Content: Guh... I won't admit defeat. I've got to do better next time.
RoleVoice.22205085_Content: Hmm, you quite fit my aesthetic.
RoleVoice.22205089_Content: Hmm, care to see my impromptu performance?
RoleVoice.22107067_Content: I’ve been ready for ages, let's get started!
RoleVoice.22137072_Content: Shh... Don't let me find you!
RoleVoice.22115137_Content: Before the law of mortal demise, you and I are equals.
RoleVoice.22137069_Content: Kanami will respond to the desires beneath the waves!
RoleVoice.22205140_Content: Thanks to you, I've deceived everyone.
RoleVoice.22998020_Content: Alert! Just five more kills until the opponent wins.
RoleVoice.22131139_Content:
Don't lose heart.
Fay says: “Failure is the mother of success.”
RoleVoice.22107139_Content:
It's alright, everyone! 
We'll get 'em tomorrow!
RoleVoice.22124140_Content:
A decisive victory!
Didn't I say that a good medic is the key to every battle?
RoleVoice.22146139_Content: I failed... I have to keep improving my skills.
RoleVoice.22109137_Content: Failure is a necessary cost for innovation.
RoleVoice.22120070_Content: It's been a while since I left the greenhouse. I could use some exercise.
RoleVoice.22110020_Content: Alright, let's go with this one!
RoleVoice.22107140_Content: Ooh, that’s lovely... whoa—can’t stop when inspiration hits!
RoleVoice.22131070_Content: This place is crowded... Fay is uncomfortable.
RoleVoice.22101139_Content: If only I fought a bit harder...
RoleVoice.22112138_Content: If there's a reward, taiyaki will do.
RoleVoice.22205114_Content: My bullets are my fervent kisses.
RoleVoice.22107073_Content: Watch and learn. This is how you paint!
RoleVoice.22205138_Content: There are always winners and losers—they lose, I win.
RoleVoice.22128137_Content: Behind every failure is an opportunity to learn...
RoleVoice.22124139_Content: Even if I'm the last one standing, I'll ensure everyone gets out safely.
RoleVoice.22205069_Content: Hold your breath, don't even blink.
RoleVoice.22115112_Content: Vivid illusions must end in awakening.
RoleVoice.22120067_Content: Please inform me of the results, Navigator.
RoleVoice.22121069_Content: String energy resonance. Embrace your destiny.
RoleVoice.22124079_Content: Ultimate aid, arriving at light speed!
RoleVoice.22133138_Content: We're one step closer to home.
RoleVoice.22105068_Content: What's the matter? You've never seen me all dressed up?
RoleVoice.22109069_Content: Someone has to bear the darkness. I don't mind being that person.
RoleVoice.22119110_Content: Surrender if you want everything to return to normal.
RoleVoice.22110077_Content: Want to take me down? Not a chance!
RoleVoice.22121074_Content: Want to pass through me? You have to pay the price!
RoleVoice.22146074_Content: May you find happiness and love.
RoleVoice.22146138_Content: I hope this war will end soon... but until that day, I'll continue giving it my all!
RoleVoice.22132077_Content: I am the one above all!
RoleVoice.22120068_Content: I don't like fighting, but I won't give up on it either.
RoleVoice.22115067_Content: I am but a piece on it.
RoleVoice.22109140_Content: We are The Scissors. We come for innovation.
RoleVoice.22132138_Content: We are The Scissors, destined to overthrow the world!
RoleVoice.22108069_Content: I will keep my word, for this is my sole purpose.
RoleVoice.22120069_Content: I will calm your mind. Focus on fighting.
RoleVoice.22205079_Content: My illusions are legion; they never dwindle.
RoleVoice.22105112_Content: You know I'll win, don't you?
RoleVoice.22133113_Content: I hear the gods comforting the dead.
RoleVoice.22115111_Content: You have no place under my rule.
RoleVoice.22109079_Content: I'll make sure your deaths serve a purpose!
RoleVoice.22133140_Content: I shall guide the way forward.
RoleVoice.22128067_Content: I shall unveil the hypocrisy of this world.
RoleVoice.22128140_Content: I'll never give up the will to fight!
RoleVoice.22119140_Content: I am the invincible high school student! Remember me!
RoleVoice.22119066_Content: I am the flame that lights up the heart of Preton.
RoleVoice.22109139_Content: I've given it my all, but it’s still nowhere near enough.
RoleVoice.22109068_Content: I pull the trigger only to welcome a new era.
RoleVoice.22109066_Content: I've been ready for a while now.
RoleVoice.22108140_Content: My faith shall guide me to the end.
RoleVoice.22121139_Content: I tried my best... Shall we have a rematch?
RoleVoice.22105066_Content: The best battlefield negotiator is a bullet!
RoleVoice.22115066_Content: The battlefield is like a chessboard.
RoleVoice.22105069_Content: Even in battle, one must maintain style!
RoleVoice.22110137_VoiceNameShort: Defeat: So Close Yet So Far
RoleVoice.22996020_Content: The enemy needs 5 more kills to win
RoleVoice.22997020_Content: The enemy needs 5 more kills to win
RoleVoice.22999020_Content: The enemy needs 5 more kills to win
RoleVoice.22131020_Content: Data shows that carrying a secondary weapon increases combat efficiency by 37%.
RoleVoice.22115114_Content: No matter how many times you try, you'll lose.
RoleVoice.22109129_Content: No need to thank me. Continue with the mission.
RoleVoice.22105070_Content: Since you're here, try to achieve glory!
RoleVoice.22131067_Content: Let's get it over with. I still have research to conduct.
RoleVoice.22115068_Content: Stars align like chess pieces, casting shadows of butterflies.
RoleVoice.22120066_Content: Let's test the latest aroma formula in combat.
RoleVoice.22137802_Content: With your support, Kanami can't lose!
RoleVoice.22119020_Content: Some are even more useful than primary weapons.
RoleVoice.22109078_Content: Destruction can be a form of salvation.
RoleVoice.22120110_Content: Weeds need to be mown regularly.
RoleVoice.22132068_Content: Come on! Let's ignite the flames of resistance!
RoleVoice.22132078_Content: Bring it! This is the roar of the rebels!
RoleVoice.22119074_Content: Face-off or flee? Have you decided?
RoleVoice.22101111_Content: After all, we are on opposite sides...
RoleVoice.22133073_Content: Behold the might of the sandstorm!
RoleVoice.22119137_Content: You win some, you lose some. Let it go.
RoleVoice.22109077_Content: No one escapes the barrel of my gun!
RoleVoice.22112069_Content: Eliminate the enemies. Is that it?
RoleVoice.22205068_Content: Let the show begin, and let gunshots replace applause!
RoleVoice.22101078_Content: Mighty Meow will not forgive you!
RoleVoice.22119069_Content: Sparks are easily extinguished. You must burn with all your might.
RoleVoice.22119077_Content: I am the foehn wind that approaches!
RoleVoice.22109070_Content: Born in daylight, hidden in shadows. Such is the duty of a sniper.
RoleVoice.22137070_Content: Compose the perfect melody with bullets!
RoleVoice.22124067_Content: Leave the medic work to me.
RoleVoice.22132139_Content: Put your faith in me, and I shall lead you into the light!
RoleVoice.22119070_Content: Achieving victory begins with believing in yourself.
RoleVoice.22128079_Content: The truth is hidden among shadows!
RoleVoice.22137801_Content: When we're done here, make to check out my new song!
RoleVoice.22133114_Content: This is the end for you.
RoleVoice.22133139_Content:
Things have gone wrong.
We must analyze this defeat.
RoleVoice.22115140_Content: Cooperation among the wise maximizes advantages.
RoleVoice.22205078_Content: Where my spirit desires to roam, there I shall be.
RoleVoice.22137140_Content: I’ve always been on the center stage!
RoleVoice.22120139_Content: The fragrance has dissipated, but the seeds remain. Don't feel discouraged.
RoleVoice.22120137_Content: Has the fragrance gone with the wind?
RoleVoice.22120073_Content: The fragrance will wash away your fatigue.
RoleVoice.22131129_Content: Fay will be rooting for you.
RoleVoice.22115078_Content: Life and death are but an impermanent illusion.
RoleVoice.22121072_Content: It's time for my snail to shine!
RoleVoice.22121079_Content: Let the mist of corrosion fill the battlefield!
RoleVoice.22120074_Content: Give this aroma blend a try.
RoleVoice.22119109_Content: Let's wrap it up. I have band practice.
RoleVoice.22128068_Content: Wake up! You have a right to know the truth.
RoleVoice.22120112_Content: Please do not interrupt my research.
RoleVoice.22119138_Content: We won! Ha-ha-ha... I got a bit carried away again...
RoleVoice.22131138_Content: We won! Our job is done.
RoleVoice.22109138_Content: The dawn of a new era is on the horizon.
RoleVoice.22115070_Content: Follow the butterfly, then step into its trap.
RoleVoice.22205074_Content: My essence transcends mere physical bounds.
RoleVoice.22115113_Content: Blindly trusting the beauty will cost your life.
RoleVoice.22120114_Content: You will be greeted not by fragrance, but by bullets.
RoleVoice.22131140_Content: It's been a lucky day, right Fay?
RoleVoice.22101073_Content: It's my turn to protect everyone!
RoleVoice.22128077_Content: The destiny of this world is to be buried here.
RoleVoice.22128138_Content: This hypocritical world... should be overthrown.
RoleVoice.22137110_Content: This counts as a performance, too!
RoleVoice.22146140_Content: This was a real team effort.
RoleVoice.22137078_Content: This performance is just for you!
RoleVoice.22110140_Content: This is Urbino's path to liberty!
RoleVoice.22146079_Content: This is my special gift for you!
RoleVoice.22107072_Content: Now this is what I call a stroke of artistry!
RoleVoice.22128020_Content: Will this weapon do the trick?
RoleVoice.22120113_Content: A warning for the naughty kids.
RoleVoice.22205129_Content: It's not comfortable lying here, you know.
RoleVoice.22119078_Content: The flames of reverstring will never scorch an ally, but will sweep away all enemies!
RoleVoice.22205077_Content: An abundance of choices can also be a burden.
RoleVoice.22107020_Content: Will this weapon do the trick?
RoleVoice.22119114_Content: Wishing you good health, see ya!
RoleVoice.22132140_Content: We are The Scissors. Remember us.
RoleVoice.22205110_Content: Nice effort, but it's time for your curtain call.
RoleVoice.22205113_Content: Apart from magic, I excel in taking your breath away.
RoleVoice.22119129_Content: You'll warm up in no time.
RoleVoice.22205112_Content: Just kidding, of course I'd pull the trigger.
RoleVoice.22205070_Content: The essence of magic is to deceive artfully.
RoleVoice.22119068_Content: (Phew) You got this, Eika. Keep it up.
